22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Gujarat%2C%20Over%20300%20Government%20Schools%20Functioning%20With%20Single%20Classroom%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%20341%20state-run%20primary%20schools%20in%20Gujarat%20functioned%20with%20single%20classrooms%20while%20more%20than%201%2C400%20posts%20of%20administrative%20officers%20in%20the%20Education%20Department%20were%20lying%20vacant%20as%20of%20December%202023%2C%20the%20government%20told%20the%20legislative%20assembly%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20facts%20were%20revealed%20in%20a%20written%20reply%20given%20by%20Education%20Minister%20Kuber%20Dindor%20to%20a%20query%20raised%20by%20Congress%20MLA%20Kirit%20Patel%20during%20Question%20Hour%20of%20the%20ongoing%20Budget%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemolition%20of%20dilapidated%20classrooms%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20sparse%20attendance%20of%20students%2C%20and%20non-availability%20of%20land%20to%20construct%20new%20classrooms%20are%20some%20of%20the%20reasons%20mentioned%20by%20the%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20assured%20the%20House%20that%20new%20classrooms%20in%20these%20schools%20will%20be%20built%20in%20phases%20%26quot%3Bas%20soon%20as%20possible%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20another%20query%20raised%20by%20MLA%20Patel%20about%20vacant%20posts%20of%20class-1%20and%20class-2%20officers%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20Education%20Service%20cadre%2C%20Dindor%20said%20781%20posts%20were%20filled%20while%201%2C459%20posts%20were%20lying%20vacant%20as%20of%20December%2031%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20these%20vacant%20posts%20will%20be%20filled%20at%20the%20earliest%20through%20promotions%20and%20direct%20recruitment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20discussion%20on%20the%20demands%20for%20grants%2C%20Mr%20Patel%20alleged%20that%20the%20quality%20of%20education%20in%20Gujarat%20under%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20is%20deteriorating%20rapidly%20and%20the%20state%20stands%20nowhere%20in%20comparison%20to%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20government%20is%20good%20at%20only%20doing%20publicity%20and%20projecting%20Gujarat%20as%20a%20model%20state%20while%20the%20reality%20is%20different.%20As%20per%20the%20Performance%20Grading%20Index%20Report%20of%202023%2C%20nearly%2025%20per%20cent%20of%20children%20studying%20in%20primary%20schools%20in%20Gujarat%20can't%20even%20read%20Gujarati%20while%2047.20%20per%20cent%20can't%20read%20English.%20Gujarat%20was%20not%20in%20the%20top%20five%20states%20which%20performed%20well%20in%20terms%20of%20education%2C%26quot%3B%20claimed%20Mr%20Patel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDindor%20said%20more%20than%2065%2C000%20smart%20classrooms%20have%20been%20built%20by%20the%20state%20government%20so%20far%20and%20another%2043%2C000%20are%20under%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnder%20the%20Mission%20Schools%20of%20Excellence%20project%2C%20we%20have%20constructed%2015%2C000%20classrooms%20in%202023-24%20while%20construction%20for%20another%2015%2C000%20classrooms%20is%20under%20progress.%20More%20than%205%2C000%20computer%20labs%20have%20been%20constructed%20and%20work%20is%20on%20for%20creating%2015%2C000%20more%20such%20labs%20in%20schools%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20said%20that%20the%20dropout%20ratio%20in%20primary%20schools%20fell%20from%2037.22%20per%20cent%20to%202.68%20per%20cent%20in%202022-23%20due%20to%20the%20efforts%20undertaken%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20ensure%20quality%20education%20in%20schools%2C%20a%20total%20of%2022%2C349%20Vidya%20Sahayak%20and%20Gyan%20Sahayak%20(contractual%20teachers)%20have%20been%20appointed%20in%20the%20year%202023-24.%20For%20the%20year%202024-25%2C%20more%20than%20Rs%202%2C785%20crore%20has%20been%20allocated%20for%20the%20upgradation%20of%20primary%20schools%20under%20the%20Mission%20Schools%20of%20Excellence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline