%20by%20the%20Aeronautical%20Development%20Establishment.%20Under%20the%20Rs%2046%2C898%20crore%20contract%20inked%20with%20Hindustan%20Aeronautics%20(HAL)%20in%20February%202021%2C%2083%20Tejas%20Mark-1A%20have%20to%20be%20delivered%20to%20the%20IAF%20in%20the%20February%202024-February%202028%20timeframe.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nawaz%20Sharif%2C%20Bilawal%20Bhutto's%20Parties%20Reach%20New%20Coalition%20Deal%20In%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20and%20the%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20have%20finally%20reached%20an%20agreement%20to%20form%20a%20new%20coalition%20government%20after%20days%20of%20intense%20negotiations%2C%20senior%20party%20leaders%20have%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20news%20conference%20late%20on%20Tuesday%20night%2C%20Pakistan%20Peoples%20Party%20(PPP)%20Chairman%20Bilawal%20Bhutto-Zardari%20announced%20that%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League-Nawaz%20(PML-N)%20President%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%2C%2072%2C%20is%20set%20to%20assume%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20once%20again.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20PPP%20co-chairman%20Asif%20Zardari%2C%2068%2C%20is%20slated%20to%20become%20the%20country's%20President%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PPP%20and%20PML-N%20have%20achieved%20the%20required%20number%2C%20and%20%5Bnow%5D%20we%20are%20in%20a%20position%20to%20form%20the%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Bilawal%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20former%20prime%20minister%20Imran%20Khan's%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20party-backed%20candidates%20and%20Sunni%20Ittehad%20Council%20(SIC)%20failed%20to%20achieve%20a%20simple%20majority%20in%20Parliament%20to%20form%20government%20in%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilawal%20hoped%20that%20the%20news%20of%20the%20political%20alliance%20with%20the%20PML-N%20to%20form%20a%20coalition%20government%20would%20lead%20to%20a%20positive%20market%20response%20as%20the%20cash-strapped%20country%20faced%20a%20hung%20Parliament%20after%20the%20February%208%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndependent%20candidates%20-%20a%20majority%20backed%20by%2071-year-old%20Khan's%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20party%20--%20won%2093%20National%20Assembly%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20occasion%2C%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20asserted%20that%20his%20PML-N%20now%20has%20the%20%26quot%3Brequired%20numbers%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20PPP%20to%20be%20in%20a%20position%20to%20form%20the%20next%20government%20as%20he%20thanked%20the%20leadership%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20for%20the%20positive%20conclusion%20to%20the%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20prime%20minister%20emphasised%20the%20unity%20between%20the%20two%20parties%2C%20noting%20that%20they%20were%20well-positioned%20to%20form%20the%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20The%20Express%20Tribune%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PML-N%20won%2075%20seats%20while%20the%20PPP%20came%20third%20with%2054%20seats.%20The%20Muttahida%20Qaumi%20Movement%20Pakistan%20(MQM-P)%20has%20also%20agreed%20to%20support%20them%20with%20their%2017%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20form%20a%20government%2C%20a%20party%20must%20win%20133%20out%20of%20265%20contested%20seats%20in%20the%20266-member%20National%20Assembly%20or%20the%20lower%20house%20of%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%2071-year-old%20Khan's%20PTI%20hit%20out%20at%20the%20newly%20cemented%20PPP%2C%20PML-N%20alliance%20as%20'PDM%202.0'%20%26quot%3BPDM%202.0%20%3D%20%23MandateThieves.%26quot%3B%20The%20announcement%20of%20the%20alliance%20came%20a%20day%20after%20the%20latest%20round%20of%20talks%20between%20the%20top%20leaders%20of%20the%20two%20parties%20ended%20inconclusively%20on%20Monday%20as%20both%20sides%20failed%20to%20reach%20a%20consensus%20on%20a%20power-sharing%20formula%20to%20f