0in%20a%20black%20suit%2C%20while%20Rani%20stunned%20in%20a%20plain%20black%20saree.%20Other%20celebrities%2C%20including%20Shahid%20Kapoor%20and%20Kareena%20Kapoor%20Khan%2C%20also%20showcased%20their%20style.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-and-rani-mukerji-share-a-warm-hug-as-they-attend-dadasaheb-phalke-international-film-festival-awards-2024-see-photos%2Farticleshow%2F107861341.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BLike%20Doomsday%26quot%3B%3A%20Gazans%20Describe%20Terrifying%20Evacuation%20From%20Hospital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGunfire%20echoed%20around%20Palestinian%20medics%2C%20patients%20and%20displaced%20people%20during%20what%20they%20described%20as%20a%20terrifying%20and%20chaotic%20night%20evacuation%20from%20Gaza's%20Nasser%20Hospital%20after%20Israeli%20forces%20rushed%20in%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurvivors%20of%20last%20week's%20assault%20on%20the%20second-biggest%20hospital%20in%20Gaza%20said%20they%20then%20faced%20a%20treacherous%20walk%20to%20safety%20through%20the%20dark%2C%20passing%20corpses%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20doctor%20said%20a%20male%20nurse%20was%20detained%20at%20an%20Israeli%20checkpoint%2C%20stripped%20naked%20and%20taken%20away%20screaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSmoke%20was%20everywhere%2C%20it%20was%20like%20doomsday%2C%20people%20running%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Doctor%20Ahmed%20al-Mughraby%2C%20head%20of%20the%20plastic%20surgery%20department%2C%20who%20fled%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMughraby%2C%20who%20has%20found%20refuge%20with%20his%20family%20in%20a%20shelter%20near%20another%20hospital%20where%20he%20now%20works%2C%20said%20Israeli%20forces%20had%20ordered%20everyone%20to%20evacuate%20except%20patients%20unable%20to%20walk%20and%20medics%20looking%20after%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetails%20of%20the%20military%20assault%20on%20Nasser%20Hospital%20have%20been%20gradually%20emerging%20as%20the%20people%20who%20fled%20or%20were%20evacuated%20reach%20Rafah%2C%20the%20last%20relatively%20safe%20place%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20about%20six%20miles%20(10%20km)%20away%20on%20the%20border%20with%20Egypt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20described%20the%20assault%20as%20a%20precision%20operation%20conducted%20by%20special%20forces%20aimed%20at%20recovering%20the%20bodies%20of%20Israeli%20hostages.%20It%20said%20there%20had%20been%20no%20obligation%20on%20patients%20and%20staff%20to%20leave%2C%20and%20efforts%20were%20made%20to%20ensure%20the%20hospital%20could%20keep%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20raid%20has%20prompted%20alarm%20among%20aid%20agencies%2C%20and%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20said%20the%20amount%20of%20damage%20was%20%26quot%3Bindescribable%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%2C%20the%20UN%20health%20agency%2C%20has%20carried%20out%20two%20evacuations%20from%20Nasser%20Hospital%20since%20Thursday%20but%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20it%20was%20concerned%20about%20nearly%20150%20patients%20and%20medics%20remaining%20there%20as%20fighting%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20besieging%20the%20hospital%2C%20Israeli%20forces%20entered%20it%20last%20Thursday%20and%20said%20they%20had%20detained%20hundreds%20of%20operatives%20hiding%20there%2C%20with%20some%20posing%20as%20hospital%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20has%20denied%20using%20the%20hospital%2C%20and%20calls%20Israel's%20allegations%20%26quot%3Blies%26quot%3B.%20The%20Health%20Ministry%20in%20Gaza%20has%20said%20Israel%20has%20detained%2070%20staff%20and%20volunteers%20working%20at%20the%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20said%20the%20hospital%20stopped%20functioning%20last%20week%20after%20the%20Israeli%20siege%20and%20raid%2C%20and%20no%20longer%20had%20electricity%20or%20running%20water%2C%20with%20medical%20waste%20and%20garbage%20creating%20a%20breeding%20ground%20for%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDrone%20Fire%2C%20%26quot%3BAggressive%20Dogs%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENasser%20Hospital%20was%20the%20biggest%20hospital%20still%20operating%20in%20Gaza%20more%20than%20four%20months%20into%20the%20war%20that%20began%20when%20fighters%20from%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20Hamas%20raided%20Israeli%20towns%20on%20Oct.%207%2C%20killing%201%2C200%20people%20and%20taking%20253%20hostages%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20tallies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20campaign%20in%20Gaza%20has%20since%20killed%20more%20than%2029%2C000%20Palestinians%2C%20health%20authorities%20in%20the%20Hamas-run%20enclave%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHakeem%20Salem%20Hussein%20Baraka%20said%20the%20Nasser%20Hospital%20orthopaedic%20department%20where%20he%20had%20been%20working%20as%20a%20volunteer%20had%20been%20destroyed%2C%20and%20that%20he%20saw%20a%20patient%20cut%20in%20two%20by%20an%20explosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaraka%20said%20a%20%26quot%3Bquadcopter%26quot%3B%20drone%20had%20fired%20at%20medical%20staff%20taking%20a%20break%20between%20shifts%20and%20%26quot%3Baggressive%26quot%3B%20dogs%20with%20cameras%20placed%20round%20their%20necks%20by%20Israel's%20military%20had%20been%20roaming%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20said%20its%20forces%20had%20fought%20%26quot%3Bcomplex%20battles%26quot%3B%20before%20entering%20the%20hospital%20compound%20and%20came%20under%20rocket%20fire%20from%20fighters%20barricaded%20inside%20the%20hospital.%20It%20said%20troops%20found%20large%20quantities%20of%20weapons%20and%20vehicles%20linked%20to%20the%20October%207%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20gave%20people%20an%20opportunity%20to%20evacuate%20before%20we%20entered%20the%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20Colonel%20Moshe%20Tetro%20told%20a%20news%20briefing.%20Asked%20whether%20there%20was%20any%20gunfire%20or%20combat%20within%20the%20hospital%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BNo%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Palestinians%20left%20the%20hospital%20before%20dawn%2C%20some%20had%20to%20wade%20through%20sewage%2C%20said%20Rasmeya%20Saleem%20Abu%20Jamoos%2C%20a%20dialysis%20patient%20who%20fled%20with%20her%20blind%20husband%2C%20Abu%20Jamoos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20among%20people%20detained%20at%20a%20military%20checkpoint%20after%20leaving%20the%20hospital%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20doctor%2C%20Mughraby%2C%20said%20his%20ward%20had%20been%20hit%20by%20Israeli%20fire%20and%20that%20he%20believed%20three%20patients%20had%20been%20killed%20in%20the%20strike.%20Reuters%20was%20unable%20to%20verify%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20and%20his%20family%20had%20left%20the%20hospital%20with%20three%20patients%20and%20some%20staff%20members%20but%20one%2C%20a%20department%20nurse%2C%20was%20stopped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20made%20him%20take%20off%20all%20his%20clothes%20so%20he%20was%20naked%20and%20they%20took%20him%20to%20detention.%20I%20could%20hear%20his%20screams%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMughraby%20said%20those%20who%20made%20it%20through%20the%20checkpoint%20then%20had%20a%20long%20walk%20across%20a%20battlefield%20to%20reach%20help.%20Some%20were%20sick%20or%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaraa%20Ahmed%20Abu%20Mustafa%2C%20who%20was%20on%20mismatching%20crutches%2C%20said%20shots%20were%20fired%20over%20their%20heads%20as%20they%20went%20and%20there%20were%20dead%20bodies%20near%20the%20hospital%20entrance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20injured%20and%20for%20one%20hour%20I%20walked%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20dangerous%20and%20the%20road%20was%20bad.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708451