%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fnikki-haley-vows-to-continue-fighting-donald-trump-in-gop-contest%2Famp_articleshow%2F107860741.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20Receives%20France's%20Highest%20Civilian%20Honour%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShashi%20Tharoor%2C%20a%20prolific%20author%20and%20a%20diplomat-turned-politician%2C%20was%20conferred%20France's%20highest%20civilian%20honour%20'Chevalier%20de%20la%20Legion%20d'honneur'%20at%20a%20ceremony%20here%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuthor%20of%20several%20books%20and%20the%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Thiruvananthapuram%2C%20Tharoor%20was%20conferred%20the%20prestigious%20award%20at%20the%20French%20Embassy%20by%20French%20Senate%20President%20Gerard%20Larcher.%20The%20French%20government%20had%20announced%20the%20award%20for%20Tharoor%2C%20a%20former%20Union%20minister%2C%20in%20August%202022%20but%20was%20conferred%20on%20him%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20highest%20French%20civilian%20award%20came%20in%20recognition%20of%20Dr%20Tharoor's%20tireless%20efforts%20to%20deepen%20Indo-French%20ties%2C%20commitment%20to%20international%20peace%20and%20cooperation%2C%20and%20as%20a%20long-standing%20friend%20of%20France%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20statement%20issued%20by%20the%20French%20Embassy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConferring%20the%20honour%20on%20Mr%20Tharoor%2C%20Chairman%20of%20the%20French%20Senate%20Larcher%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThrough%20his%20outstanding%20career%20as%20a%20diplomat%2C%20author%20and%20politician%2C%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20has%20embraced%20the%20world%20with%20a%20thirst%20for%20knowledge%20and%20an%20intelligence%20that%20has%20led%20him%20to%20live%20several%20lifetimes%20in%20one%2C%20and%20all%20of%20them%20in%20service%20to%20India%20and%20a%20better%20world.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BDr%20Tharoor%20is%20also%20a%20true%20friend%20of%20France%2C%20a%20Francophone%20with%20a%20keen%20understanding%20of%20France%20and%20its%20culture.%20Through%20this%20award%2C%20which%20I%20have%20the%20privilege%20to%20confer%2C%20the%20French%20Republic%20recognises%20your%20accomplishments%2C%20your%20friendship%2C%20your%20love%20of%20France%2C%20your%20commitment%20to%20a%20fairer%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Larcher%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReceiving%20the%20recognition%2C%20Mr%20Tharoor%20said%20he%20was%20immensely%20honoured%20to%20accept%20the%20Chevalier%20de%20la%20Legion%20d'Honneur%20(Knight%20of%20the%20Legion%20of%20Honour).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20someone%20who%20admires%20France%2C%20its%20people%2C%20their%20refinement%2C%20their%20language%2C%20and%20their%20culture%2C%20especially%20their%20literature%20and%20cinema%2C%20I%20am%20deeply%20humbled%20to%20be%20conferred%20your%20country's%20highest%20civilian%20honour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20my%20mind%2C%20the%20conferral%20of%20this%20award%20to%20an%20Indian%20is%20an%20acknowledgement%20of%20the%20deepening%20of%20Franco-Indian%20relations%20and%20the%20continuity%20of%20the%20warmth%20that%20has%20been%20a%20feature%20of%20this%20relationship%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Tharoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20honour%2C%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20is%20not%20just%20a%20celebration%20of%20individual%20achievement%20but%20%26quot%3Balso%20reflects%20the%20collective%20efforts%20of%20both%20our%20countries%20in%20fostering%20cultural%20exchange%20and%20diplomatic%20ties%2C%20a%20relationship%20forged%20through%20the%20pillars%20of%20mutual%20respect%2C%20admiration%2C%20and%20collaboration%20that%20have%20allowed%20this%20unique%20association%20to%20flourish%20over%20the%20years%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20look%20forward%20to%20continuing%20my%20own%20efforts%20towards%20nurturing%20this%20friendship%20and%20promoting%20further%20cooperation%20between%20India%20and%20France%2C%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20our%20shared%20global%20community%20and%20to%20safeguard%20the%20common%20values%20that%20underpin%20our%20basic%20humanity%2C%26quot%3B%20Tharoor%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20address%2C%20the%20Congress%20MP%20also%20recounted%20the%20defining%20moment%20of%20his%20French%20trip%20in%202002%20for%20the%20Belles%20Etrangeres%20sponsored%20by%20the%20Centre%20National%20du%20Livre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20Indian%20group%20of%20writers%2C%20returning%20from%20a%20reception%20at%20the%20majestic%20Hotel%20de%20Ville%2C%20found%20themselves%20accidental%20witnesses%20to%20the%20interment%20of%20the%20nineteenth-century%20novelist%20Alexandre%20Dumas%2C%20more%20than%20a%20century%20after%20his%20death%2C%20in%20the%20magnificently%20lit%20Pantheon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Roman%20columns%20of%20this%20great%20Parisian%20monument%20were%20bathed%20in%20purple%2C%20red%20and%20blue%20light%2C%20a%20military%20band%20played%20outside%2C%20while%20an%20honour%20guard%20escorted%20the%20coffin%20of%20the%20author%20of%20The%20Three%20Musketeers%20to%20its%20final%20resting%20place%2C%20Tharoor%20recounted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnanthamurthy%2C%20the%20veteran%20novelist%20who%20was%20the%20doyen%20of%20our%20group%2C%20put%20it%20simply%20to%20me.%20'The%20French%2C'%20he%20said%2C%20really%20know%20how%20to%20honour%20their%20writers'.%20May%20I%20now%20add%3A%20I%20am%20glad%20they%20are%20honouring%20ours%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Tharoor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstituted%20in%201802%20by%20Napoleon%20Bonaparte%2C%20the%20Legion%20d'honneur%20is%20the%20highest%20civilian%20award%20given%20by%20the%20French%20Republic%20for%20outstanding%20service%20to%20France%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20nationality%20of%20the%20recipients.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President%20of%20the%20French%20Republic%20is%20the%20Grand%20Master%20of%20the%20Order%20of%20the%20Legion%20of%20Honour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20envoy%20to%20India%20Thierry%20Mathou%2C%20India's%20G20%20sherpa%20Amitabh%20Kant%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Anand%20Sharma%2C%20among%20others%2C%20attended%20the%20ceremony.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708448940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fm0h24sk8_shashi-tharoor_625x300_29_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-mp-shashi-tharoor-conferred-frances-highest-civilian-honour-chevalier-de-la-legion-dhonneur-5095659%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shashi%20Tharoor%2C%20a%20prolific%20author%20and%20a%20diplomat-turned-politician%2C%20was%20conferred%20France's%20highest%20civilian%20honour%20%26quot%3BChevalier%20de%20la%20Legion%20d'honneur%26quot%3B%20at%20a%20ceremony%20here%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-mp-shashi-tharoor-conferred-frances-highest-civilian-honour-chevalier-de-la-legion-dhonneur-5095659%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-mp-shashi-tharoor-conferred-frances-highest-civilian-honour-chevalier-de-la-legion-dhonneur-5095659%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-mp-shashi-tharoor-conferred-frances-highest-civilian-honour-chevalier-de-la-legion-dhonneur-5095659%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe're%20Open%26quot%3B%3A%20S%20Jaishankar%20On%20India%20Mediating%20To%20End%20Russia-Ukraine%20War%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EExternal%20Affairs%20Minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20has%20indicated%20that%20India%20was%20open%20to%20considering%20playing%20the%20role%20of%20a%20mediator%20to%20end%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20conflict%20if%20approached%20but%20noted%20that%20New%20Delhi%20does%20not%20believe%20it%20should%20initiate%20anything%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20German%20economic%20daily%20Handelsblatt%2C%20he%20also%20said%20that%20following%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%2C%20India's%20energy%20suppliers%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20gave%20priority%20to%20supplying%20petroleum%20products%20to%20Europe%20that%20paid%20higher%20prices%20and%20New%20Delhi%20did%20not%20have%20any%20option%20but%20to%20procure%20Russian%20crude%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20asserted%20that%20just%20as%20India%20does%20not%20expect%20Europe%20to%20have%20a%20view%20of%20China%20that%20is%20identical%20to%20New%20Delhi's%2C%20Europe%20should%20understand%20that%20India%20cannot%20have%20a%20view%20of%20Russia%20that%20is%20identical%20to%20the%20European%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20India%20has%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bstable%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bvery%20friendly%26quot%3B%20relationship%20with%20Russia%2C%20and%20that%20Moscow%20never%20hurt%20New%20Delhi's%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20had%20a%20politically%20and%20militarily%20much%20more%20difficult%20relationship%20with%20China%2C%20for%20example%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20India's%20continuing%20military%20cooperation%20with%20Russia%20notwithstanding%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%2C%20Jaishankar%20said%20it%20is%20going%20on%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20many%20Western%20countries%20have%20long%20preferred%20to%20supply%20Pakistan%20and%20not%20India.%26quot%3B%20Jaishankar%20said%20India%20is%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20convinced%2C%20and%20are%20publicly%20committed%20to%20bringing%20the%20conflict%20to%20an%20end%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20suffering%20from%20this%20conflict.%20I%20don't%20know%20exactly%20how%20it%20will%20end%2C%20we're%20not%20deep%20enough%20into%20the%20process%20to%20know%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20that%20isn't%20a%20reason%20why%20India%20could%20be%20a%20mediator%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BTheoretically%2C%20yes.%20We%20have%20already%20helped%20with%20very%20specific%20issues.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Turkey%20negotiated%20the%20corridor%20through%20the%20Black%20Sea%2C%20for%20example.%20And%20we%20were%20very%20supportive%20of%20the%20inspections%20by%20the%20International%20Atomic%20Energy%20Agency%2C%20IAEA%2C%20of%20the%20Zaporizhzhya%20nuclear%20power%20plant%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWherever%20we%20can%20help%2C%20we%20are%20happy%20to%20do%20so.%20We%20are%20open%20when%20we%20are%20approached.%20However%2C%20we%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20we%20should%20initiate%20anything%20in%20this%20direction%20on%20our%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETurkey%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20activating%20the%20corridor%20to%20transport%20grain%20from%20Ukraine%20to%20various%20world%20markets%20as%20Russia%20had%20blocked%20it%20following%20the%20escalation%20of%20its%20conflict%20with%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20also%20strongly%20justified%20India's%20procurement%20of%20Russian%20crude%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20fighting%20started%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Europe%20shifted%20a%20large%20part%20of%20its%20energy%20procurement%20to%20the%20Middle%20East%20--%20until%20then%20the%20main%20supplier%20for%20India%20and%20other%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20should%20we%20have%20done%3F%20In%20many%20cases%2C%20our%20Middle-East%20suppliers%20gave%20priority%20to%20Europe%20because%20Europe%20paid%20higher%20prices.%20Either%20we%20would%20have%20had%20no%20energy%20because%20everything%20would%20have%20gone%20to%20them.%20Or%20we%20would%20have%20ended%20up%20paying%20a%20lot%20more%20because%20you%20were%20paying%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20certain%20way%2C%20we%20stabilised%20the%20energy%20market%20that%20way%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20response%20came%20when%20asked%20about%20criticism%20in%20Europe%20against%20India%20that%20its%20procurement%20of%20Russian%20crude%20oil%20is%20detrimental%20to%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20Western%20sanctions%20imposed%20on%20Moscow%20for%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20external%20affairs%20minister%20argued%20that%20if%20no%20one%20had%20bought%20the%20crude%20oil%20from%20Russia%20and%20everyone%20had%20procured%20it%20from%20other%20countries%2C%20prices%20on%20the%20energy%20market%20would%20have%20shot%20up%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGlobal%20inflation%20would%20have%20been%20much%20higher%20--%20and%20that%20would%20have%20been%20a%20huge%20political%20issue%20in%20lower-income%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Europe%20had%20wanted%20to%20maximize%20the%20damage%20at%20the%20time%2C%20it%20would%20have%20had%20to%20stop%20all%20economic%20relations%20with%20Russia%20completely.%20But%20it%20didn't%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jaishankar%20said%20if%20Europe%20was%20so%20convinced%20and%20the%20principles%20were%20so%20important%2C%20why%20did%20it%20allow%20relations%20to%20end%20%26quot%3Bgently%26quot%3B%3F%20%26quot%3BWhy%20were%20there%20exceptions%20for%20pipeline%20gas%2C%20for%20individual%20countries%20and%20so%20on%3F%20That's%20what%20governments%20do%2C%20they%20manage%20politics%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20consequences%20for%20their%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20India%20would%20have%20liked%20support%20from%20Europe%20in%20the%20border%20conflict%20with%20China%20in%202020%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20%26quot%3BMy%20point%20is%3A%20just%20as%20I%20do%20not%20expect%20Europe%20to%20have%20a%20view%20of%20China%20that%20is%20identical%20to%20mine%2C%20Europe%20should%20understand%20that%20I%20cannot%20have%20a%20view%20of%20Russia%20that%20is%20identical%20to%20the%20European%20one.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BLet%20us%20accept%20that%20there%20are%20natural%20differences%20in%20relationships%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20the%20Indo-Russian%20engagement%20is%20a%20burden%20on%20the%20India-Europe%20ties%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%20everyone%20conducts%20a%20relationship%20based%20on%20their%20past%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20look%20at%20the%20history%20of%20India%20post-independence%2C%20Russia%20has%20never%20hurt%20our%20interests.%20The%20relations%20of%20powers%20like%20Europe%2C%20the%20US%2C%20China%20or%20Japan%20with%20Russia%2C%20they%20have%20all%20seen%20ups%20and%20downs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20had%20a%20stable%20and%20always%20very%20friendly%20relationship%20with%20Russia.%20And%20our%20relationship%20with%20Russia%20today%20is%20based%20on%20this%20experience.%20For%20others%2C%20things%20were%20different%2C%20and%20conflicts%20may%20have%20shaped%20the%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20India%20recently%20agreeing%20on%20more%20arms%20cooperation%20with%20Russia%20and%20whether%20the%20country%20is%20still%20the%20most%20important%20arms%20supplier%20for%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Mr%20Jaishankar%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIn%20terms%20of%20inventory%2C%20yes%2C%20because%20many%20Western%20countries%20have%20long%20preferred%20to%20supply%20Pakistan%20and%20not%20India.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BBut%20that%20has%20changed%20in%20the%20past%2010%20or%2015%20years%20with%20the%20US%2C%20for%20example%2C%20and%20our%20new%20purchases%20have%20diversified%20with%20the%20US%2C%20Russia%2C%20France%20and%20Israel%20as%20the%20main%20suppliers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.