Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20site%20in%20the%20Israeli-annexed%20Old%20City%20of%20Jerusalem%20is%20Islam's%20third-holiest%20and%20Judaism's%20most%20sacred%2C%20known%20to%20Jews%20as%20the%20Temple%20Mount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20is%20yet%20to%20officially%20decide%20on%20restrictions%20for%20Muslim%20worshippers%20during%20Ramadan%2C%20expected%20to%20start%20around%20March%2010%2C%20but%20proposals%20to%20limit%20numbers%20have%20already%20sparked%20angry%20backlash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Israel's%20hard-right%20National%20Security%20Minister%20Itamar%20Ben%20Gvir%20argued%20that%20Palestinian%20residents%20of%20the%20occupied%20West%20Bank%20%26quot%3Bshould%20not%20be%20allowed%26quot%3B%20entry%20to%20Jerusalem%20to%20pray%20during%20Ramadan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsually%2C%20Muslims%20in%20their%20tens%20and%20even%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20pray%20and%20break%20their%20fast%20at%20the%20compound%2C%20seized%20by%20Israel%20in%201967%20and%20later%20annexed%20alongside%20the%20rest%20of%20east%20Jerusalem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202000%2C%20a%20visit%20there%20by%20Israel's%20then-opposition%20leader%20Ariel%20Sharon%20sparked%20Palestinian%20riots%20which%20precipitated%20the%20bloody%2C%20years-long%20second%20intifada%2C%20or%20uprising.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolent%20clashes%20also%20broke%20out%20during%20Ramadan%20last%20year%20and%20in%202022%2C%20after%20in%20May%202021%20the%20storming%20of%20the%20mosque%20by%20Israeli%20police%20spiralled%20into%20a%20brief%20but%20deadly%20war%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20look%20at%20recent%20developments%20around%20Al-Aqsa%20as%20Israel%20is%20fighting%20in%20the%20bloodiest%20ever%20Gaza%20war%2C%20sparked%20by%20Hamas's%20October%207%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20does%20Ramadan%20cause%20tension%20in%20Jerusalem%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolence%20during%20Ramadan%20has%20often%20revolved%20around%20Israel's%20policing%20of%20the%20compound%2C%20including%20restrictions%20on%20Palestinian%20access%2C%20as%20well%20as%20any%20moves%20that%20appear%20to%20challenge%20the%20historical%20status%20quo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20an%20agreement%20with%20Jordan%2C%20the%20custodian%20of%20the%20mosque%2C%20Jews%20can%20access%20the%20compound%20but%20not%20pray%20there%2C%20something%20which%20infuriates%20hard-right%20Israelis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20clashes%20between%20Palestinians%20and%20Israeli%20security%20forces%20have%20rocked%20the%20Al-Aqsa%20mosque%20compound%20during%20Ramadan%2C%20with%20the%20Israelis%20storming%20the%20mosque%20each%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20clashes%20and%20the%20demolition%20of%20Palestinian%20homes%20in%20east%20Jerusalem%20set%20off%20Jewish-Arab%20violence%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20several%20days%20of%20clashes%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20Hamas%20launched%20hundreds%20of%20rockets%20into%20Israel%2C%20triggering%20an%2011-day%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Ben%20Gvir%2C%20who%20leads%20a%20hard-right%20party%20advocating%20Jewish%20control%20of%20the%20compound%2C%20said%20Palestinian%20residents%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20%26quot%3Bshould%20not%20be%20allowed%26quot%3B%20entry%20to%20Jerusalem%20to%20pray%20during%20Ramadan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20take%20risks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20cannot%20have%20women%20and%20children%20hostage%20in%20Gaza%20and%20allow%20celebrations%20for%20Hamas%20on%20the%20Temple%20Mount.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20media%20have%20reported%20discussions%20of%20a%20cap%20on%20the%20number%20of%20worshippers%2C%20but%20no%20official%20decision%20has%20yet%20been%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20reactions%20has%20Ben%20Gvir%20triggered%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYair%20Lapid%2C%20a%20former%20prime%20minister%20and%20centrist%20opposition%20leader%20who%20rejected%20an%20offer%20to%20join%20the%20war%20cabinet%2C%20accused%20Ben%20Gvir%20of%20being%20a%20political%20arsonist.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmad%20Tibi%2C%20leader%20of%20one%20of%20the%20Israeli%20parliament's%20Arab-majority%20parties%2C%20called%20the%20minister's%20proposal%20a%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20infringement%20on%20the%20freedom%20of%20worship%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Israel%20Hayom%20newspaper%20said%20Ben%20Gvir%20was%20proposing%20a%20%26quot%3Bcynical%20political%20gesture%20based%20on%20an%20extremely%20dangerous%20and%20volatile%20ideology%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20backfire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Gaza%20war%20on%20October%207%2C%20the%20Israeli%20army%20has%20tried%20to%20keep%20Gaza%20separate%20from%20other%20Palestinian%20areas%20to%20avoid%20a%20flare-up%20in%20Jerusalem%2C%20the%20West%20Bank%20or%20Arab%20cities%20and%20towns%20inside%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Al-Aqsa%20mosque%20compound%20is%20a%20powerful%20symbol%20for%20religious%20and%20secular%20Palestinians%20alike%2C%20and%20defending%20it%20is%20something%20with%20the%20potential%20to%20stir%20up%20widespread%20unrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClosing%20the%20compound%2C%20said%20Israel%20Hayom%2C%20would%20be%20an%20%26quot%3Bunnecessary%20provocation%20that%20would%20ultimately%20serve%20the%20interests%20of%20Hamas%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%20denounced%20Ben%20Gvir's%20remarks%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20violation%20of%20freedom%20of%20worship%26quot%3B%20and%20an%20%26quot%3Bintensification%26quot%3B%20of%20what%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20called%20%26quot%3Breligious%20wars%26quot%3B%20waged%20against%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Islamist%20group%20called%20its%20surprise%20October%207%20attack%20on%20Israel%20which%20sparked%20the%20war%20%26quot%3BAl-Aqsa%20Flood%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20has%20said%20that%20the%20fighting%20is%2C%20in%20part%2C%20about%20defending%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20there%20be%20a%20Gaza%20truce%20before%20Ramadan%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInternational%20mediators%20--%20Qatar%2C%20Egypt%20and%20the%20United%20States%20--%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20secure%20a%20ceasefire%20agreement%20before%20the%20start%20of%20Ramadan%20to%20halt%20the%20fighting%20for%20several%20weeks%20and%20win%20the%20release%20of%20at%20least%20some%20of%20the%20130%20hostages%20Israel%20says%20remain%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20the%20army%20would%20carry%20out%20a%20%26quot%3Bpowerful%26quot%3B%20operation%20in%20Rafah%2C%20Gaza's%20southernmost%20city%20and%20last%20major%20population%20centre%20spared%20by%20Israel's%20ground%20invasion%2C%20where%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20territory's%20population%20have%20taken%20shelter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20war%20cabinet%20member%20Benny%20Gantz%20warned%20this%20week%20that%20%26quot%3Bif%20by%20Ramadan%20the%20hostages%20are%20not%20home%2C%20the%20fighting%20will%20continue%20everywhere%20to%20include%20the%20Rafah%20area%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGantz%20was%20defence%20minister%20in%202014%2C%20when%20Israel%20launched%20its%20last%20ground%20incursion%20in%20Gaza%2C%20which%20also%20took%20place%20during%20Ramadan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708447680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Fhf2uer78_al-aqsa-mosque_625x300_03_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftensions-over-jerusalems-al-aqsa-mosque-as-ramadan-nears-5095549%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20Gaza%20war%20rages%20and%20the%20Muslim%20holy%20month%20of%20Ramadan%20nears%2C%20concern%20has%20grown%20over%20potential%20tensions%20at%20Jerusalem's%20Al-Aqsa%20mosque%20comp