%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maratha%20Quota%20Bill%20Draft%20Similar%20To%20Bill%20Struck%20Down%20By%20Court%3A%20Sharad%20Pawar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENCP%20founder%20Sharad%20Pawar%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20the%20draft%20of%20the%20Maratha%20quota%20bill%20passed%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20legislature%20was%20similar%20to%20the%20earlier%20legislation%20which%20could%20not%20stand%20the%20legal%20scrutiny%2C%20and%20added%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20decide%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20fresh%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20legislature%20has%20unanimously%20passed%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Socially%20and%20Educationally%20Backward%20Bill%202024%20granting%20a%2010%20per%20cent%20reservation%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community%20in%20government%20jobs%20and%20education%20under%20a%20new%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20draft%20of%20the%20bill%20cleared%20by%20the%20state%20legislature%20today%20is%20the%20same%20as%20that%20of%20the%20one%20presented%20before%20the%20apex%20court.%20We%20need%20to%20see%20what%20happens%20to%20the%20fresh%20bill%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20Pawar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20met%20Kolhapur%20royal%20Chhatrapati%20Shahu%20Maharaj%20at%20his%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bill%20passed%20today%20is%20exactly%20like%20the%20bills%20cleared%20by%20the%20previous%20governments.%20Those%20bills%20could%20not%20stand%20the%20legal%20scrutiny%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pawar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20attempts%20by%20state%20governments%20to%20introduce%20the%20reservation%20for%20Marathas%20have%20been%20struck%20down%20by%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20just%20ahead%20of%20elections%20in%202014%2C%20the%20then%20Congress%20government%20under%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%20issued%20an%20ordinance%20implementing%20a%2016%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20Marathas.%20The%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20struck%20it%20down%2C%20citing%20the%2050%20per%20cent%20limit%20imposed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20the%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20government%20announced%20a%2016%20per%20cent%20reservation%20for%20Marathas%2C%20which%20was%20struck%20down%20by%20the%20top%20court%20in%202021%20as%20it%20breached%20the%2050%20per%20cent%20quota%20ceiling%2C%20and%20that%20there%20was%20no%20'extraordinary%20circumstance'%20for%20justification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20our%20government%20was%20in%20power%2C%20the%20reservation%20for%20Marathas%20was%20struck%20down%20at%20the%20High%20Court%20level.%20It%20survived%20the%20High%20Court%20scrutiny%20when%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20was%20in%20power%2C%20but%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20rejected%20it.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20decide%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20bill%20passed%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pawar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20predicting%20the%20legal%20outcome%20is%20not%20possible%2C%20but%20the%20past%20rulings%20of%20courts%20were%20not%20conducive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQueried%20about%20activist%20Manoj%20Jarange's%20stand%20that%20Marathas%20should%20get%20the%20reservation%20under%20the%20OBC%20category%2C%20Pawar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BJarange%20has%20called%20a%20meeting%20tomorrow%20wherein%20he%20is%20likely%20to%20clarify%20his%20position%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20Jaranage%2C%20who%20led%20the%20agitation%20on%20this%20issue%2C%20will%20be%20speaking%20about%20the%20quota%20decision%20tomorrow%2C%20it%20is%20not%20appropriate%20to%20speak%20on%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708447080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fu6ftglio_sharad-pawar-ani_625x300_02_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaratha-quota-bill-draft-si