%20among%20the%20coworkers%2C%20who%20each%20took%20home%20a%20little%20over%20%241%2C100%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Boyd%20claimed%20trouble%20had%20started%20to%20emerge%20inside%20the%20restaurant%20days%20after%20receiving%20the%20substantial%20tip%20and%20that%20management%20had%20ordered%20her%20to%20take%20that%20Sunday%20off%20as%20a%20mental%20health%20day.%20She%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20management%20had%20contacted%20her%20late%20on%20Sunday%20and%20instructed%20her%20to%20take%20Monday%20off%20as%20well.%20She%20then%20sent%20a%20message%20to%20the%20restaurant%20on%20Monday%20to%20ask%20if%20she%20was%20being%20asked%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20professional%20way%20to%20not%20come%20back.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BOne%20week%20I'm%20such%20an%20amazing%2C%20hardworking%20employee%2C%20awesome%20mother%20...%20couldn't%20have%20happened%20to%20a%20better%20person.%20Now%2C%20I'm%20without%20a%20job%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20I%20was%2015%20years%20old%2C%26quot%3B%20her%20now-deleted%20Facebook%20post%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Mason%20Jar%20Cafe%20refuted%20these%20claims%20and%20said%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bnothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20tip%26quot%3B.%20The%20restaurant%20took%20to%20Facebook%20and%20issued%20a%20clarification%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20say%20it%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20tip.%20She%20did%20receive%20the%20entire%20tip%2C%20she%20did%20not%20pay%20taxes%20on%20it%20(the%20business%20did).%20Yes%2C%20she%20shared%20the%20tip%20at%20the%20request%20of%20the%20man%20that%20left%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20husband%20and%20wife%20owners%20Able%20Martinez%20and%20Jayme%20Cousins%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fmasonjarcafe210%252Fposts%252Fpfbid0uzUuFwT4jjWwusJbuGTXE7uACDtdwxH8Nzm6h4U77aBrjUAUmReo89FudPKmvDfgl%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%2