%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20US%20Firm%20Is%20Paying%20Employees%20To%20Hang%20Out%2C%20But%20There's%20A%20Small%20Catch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20unique%20initiative%2C%20a%20%243.5%20billion%20cloud-based%20security%20company%20in%20the%20US%20is%20paying%20its%20employees%20to%20socialise%C2%A0with%20each%20other.%20The%20program%20that%20started%20last%20April%20at%C2%A0Verkada%2C%20a%20California-based%20firm%2C%20lets%20three%20or%20more%20employees%20go%20out%20for%20food%20and%20drinks%20after%203%20pm%20at%20the%20company's%20expense%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffortune.com%2F2024%2F02%2F20%2Fverkada-ceo-filip-kaliszan-security-company-paying-workers-socialize-only-in-threes%2F%5C%22%3EFortune%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20Dubbed%20the%20'3-3-3'%2C%20the%20perk%20lets%C2%A0employees%20expense%20up%20to%20%2430%20in%20food%20and%20drinks%20if%20they%20go%20out%2C%20in%20groups%20of%20at%20least%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVerkada's%20CEO%20Filip%20Kaliszan%20recently%20went%20viral%20in%20a%20TikTok%20discussing%20the%203-3-3%20perk%20on%20a%20podcast.%20''The%20idea%20is%20it's%20the%20afternoon%20and%20three%20people%20go%20out%20and%20hang%20out%20together%2C%20chances%20are%20you'll%20talk%20about%20something%20relevant%20or%20work-related%2C%20and%20ultimately%20that%20will%20benefit%20us%2C''%20Mr%20Kaliszan%20said%20in%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%201%2C800%20of%20Verkada's%20employees%20have%20participated%20in%20the%20program%20at%20least%20once.%C2%A0The%20CEO%20told%20%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20such%20kind%20of%20interaction%20is%20crucial%20for%20Verkada%20to%20stay%20competitive%20in%20an%20industry%20with%20tech%20companies%20that%20are%20worth%20%24100%20billion%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20program%20requires%C2%A0no%20pre-approval%2C%20but%C2%A0employees%20are%20required%20to%20post%20a%20photo%20in%20the%20%26quot%3B3-3-3%26quot%3B%20Slack%20channel%20when%20they're%20done%20with%20their%20outing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20program%20was%20officially%20launched%20in%20April%20last%20year%2C%20employees%20could%20still%20go%20for%20drinks%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20company%2C%20but%20they%20didn't%20know%20that.%20So%2C%20the%20firm%20decided%20to%20promote%20it%20in%20a%20better%20way%20by%C2%A0advertising%20the%20program%20on%20posters%20around%20the%20office%20and%20in%20elevators.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20about%20the%20money%20it%20wasn't%20about%20the%20budget.%20It%20was%20about%20everyone%20knowing%20that%20this%20is%20something%20they%20can%20do%20and%20then%20everyone%20getting%20excited%20about%20it%2C''%C2%A0Mr%20Kaliszan%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20quickly%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20and%20many%20praised%20the%20company%20for%20encouraging%C2%A0team%20bonding%20and%20friendships%20outside%20of%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20''That%20is%20a%20lot%20better%20use%20of%20money%20then%20like%20a%20team%20building%20exercise%20or%20hiring%20a%20speaker.''%20Another%20commented%2C%20''Building%20work%20relationships%20and%20networking%20is%20a%20necessary%20skill%20so%20I'm%20glad%20they%20are%20prioritizing%20and%20paying%20for%20it.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708443600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fr1o1agpo_office-employees_625x300_20_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fthis-us-firm-is-paying-employees-to-socialise-after-3-pm-but-theres-a-small-catch-5094997%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20'3-3-3'%20perk%20lets%20employees%20spend%20up%20to%20%2430%20on%20food%20and%20drinks%20if%20they%20go%20out%2C%20in%20groups%20of%20at%20least%20three.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fthis-us-firm-is-paying-employees-to