ly%E2%80%99%3A%20US%20Official%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20201533%2FRichard-.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20senior%20US%20administration%20official%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20(February%2020)%20that%20India%20is%20taking%20the%20allegations%20of%20Indian%20officials%E2%80%99%20involvement%20in%20the%20thwarted%20plot%20to%20kill%20a%20Sikh%20separatist%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20seriously%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20the%20US%20is%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20findings%20of%20the%20high-level%20inquiry%20established%20to%20investigate%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20November%2C%20US%20prosecutors%20unsealed%20an%20indictment%20which%20charged%20an%20Indian%20national%20named%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20for%20attempting%20to%20hire%20a%20hitman%20to%20kill%20the%20counsel%20for%20a%20pro-Khalistan%20group%2C%20Sikhs%20for%20Justice%2C%20that%20is%20banned%20by%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20charges%20also%20claimed%20that%20Gupta%20was%20recruited%20by%20an%20Indian%20government%20official.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGupta%20was%20arrested%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20in%20June%20last%20year%20and%20is%20currently%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpannun-murder-plot-nikhil-guptas-extradition-stayed-till-constitutional-courts-ruling-says-czech%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efacing%20extradition%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20as%20the%20indictment%20was%20made%20public%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20had%20set%20up%20a%20high-level%20committee%20to%20look%20into%20the%20charges.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20issue%20that%20was%20raised%2C%20look%2C%20we%20raised%20our%20concerns%20with%20the%20government%20of%20India.%20There%20is%20a%20committee%20of%20inquiry%20looking%20into%20the%20matter%20and%20we%20will%20stay%20engaged%20with%20the%20government%20and%20look%20forward%20to%20their%20findings%20and%20they%E2%80%99ve%20taken%20it%20very%20seriously.%20And%20we%E2%80%99re%20grateful%20for%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20US%20deputy%20secretary%20of%20state%20Richard%20Verma%20at%20an%20interaction%20organised%20by%20the%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%20think%20tank%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20chair%20of%20the%20powerful%20US%20senate%20foreign%20affairs%20committee%2C%20Ben%20Cardin%2C%20said%20that%20he%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foreign.senate.gov%2Fpress%2Fdem%2Frelease%2Fchair-cardin-statement-on-sale-of-mq-9-drones-to-india%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egiven%20his%20approval%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20sale%20of%20military%20drones%20to%20India%20only%20after%20getting%20assurances%20from%20White%20House%20that%20the%20charges%20are%20being%20%E2%80%9Cthoroughly%E2%80%9D%20investigated%20and%20that%20there%20is%20%E2%80%9Ccredible%20accountability%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708440665000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20201533%2FRichard-.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-takes-allegations-of-official-involvement-in-pannun-plot-very-seriously%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20deputy%20secretary%20of%20state%20Richard%20Verma%20made%20the%20remarks%20at%20an%20interaction%20organised%20by%20the%20Observer%20Research%20Foundation%20think%20tank%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-takes-allegations-of-official-involvement-in-pannun-plot-very-seriously%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Navalny's%20mother%20appeals%20to%20Putin%20to%20release%2