20One%20BJP%20MLA%20allegedly%20called%20a%20Sikh%20IPS%20officer%20present%20there%20a%20%E2%80%9CKhalistani%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20criticised%20the%20state%20government%E2%80%99s%20use%20of%20Section%20144%20%E2%80%93%20which%20restricts%20public%20assembly%20%E2%80%93%20calling%20it%20unnecessary%20and%20contributing%20to%20the%20rising%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20came%20after%20police%20initially%20blocked%20delegations%20led%20by%20BJP%20leader%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20and%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%E2%80%99s%20Brinda%20Karat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20MLAs%20led%20by%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20visit%20Sandeshkhali%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdhikari%2C%20finally%20entering%20Sandeshkhali%20on%20his%20third%20attempt%2C%20met%20with%20the%20villagers%2C%20listened%20to%20their%20concerns%20about%20the%20alleged%20sexual%20assault%20and%20land%20grabbing%20and%20offered%20his%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20visited%20the%20home%20of%20Bikash%20Sinha%2C%20the%20BJP%20leader%20who%20was%20released%20on%20bail%20last%20week%20and%20then%20re-arrested%20immediately%20after%20apparently%20in%20an%20%E2%80%9Cold%20case%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20his%20visit%2C%20Adhikari%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20finally%20spoken%20to%20the%20victims%20here.%20Women%20have%20been%20sexually%20assaulted%2C%20and%20tribals%20have%20had%20their%20lands%20forcefully%20taken.%20I%20urged%20them%20to%20pursue%20justice%20through%20the%20legal%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20absconding%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CShahjahan%20is%20still%20roaming%20around%20here.%20If%20he%20attempts%20to%20escape%20to%20Bangladesh%2C%20he%20must%20be%20apprehended%20forcefully.%20The%20BSF%20%5BBorder%20Security%20Force%5D%20needs%20to%20stay%20alert.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20a%20photograph%20of%20Shahjahan%20with%20Suvendu%20Adhikari%20when%20the%20latter%20was%20in%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20become%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECPI(M)%20leaders%20meet%20women%20protesters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECPI(M)%20politburo%20member%20Brinda%20Karat%20also%20led%20a%20delegation%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Democratic%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Association%20to%20Sandeshkhali%20and%20spoke%20to%20women%20reportedly%20affected%20by%20recent%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20accompanied%20by%20Kaninika%20Ghosh%2C%20who%20was%20stopped%20by%20the%20police%20from%20entering%20Sandeshkhali%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20personally%20spoke%20with%20the%20women%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20and%20they%20confirmed%20that%20all%20the%20allegations%20are%20accurate.%20They%20revealed%20that%20they%20did%20not%20report%20this%20to%20the%20police%20because%2C%20when%20they%20attempted%20to%20do%20so%2C%20the%20police%20at%20that%20station%20instructed%20them%20to%20inform%20Trinamool%20leaders%20first%20before%20filing%20a%20complaint!%E2%80%9D%20Karat%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20region%20has%20a%20large%20population%20of%20migrant%20workers%20and%20the%20ruling%20party%20exploited%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20disturbing%20to%20learn%20about%20these%20atrocities%20against%20women%2C%20and%20the%20female%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20dismisses%20it%20as%20a%20conspiracy%20without%20conducting%20any%20investigation.%20The%20entire%20area%20is%20gripped%20by%20fear.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20criticism%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Kunal%20Ghosh%20once%20again%20labelled%20it%20as%20drama%20concocted%20to%20disturb%20the%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr