ing%20lands%20owned%20by%20tribal%20villagers%2C%20in%20violation%20of%20legal%20formalities%2C%20appears%20to%20be%20established%20on%20a%20prima%20facie%20basis.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEditors%E2%80%99%20Guild%20of%20India%20releases%20statement%20on%20journalist%E2%80%99s%20arrest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Editors%E2%80%99%20Guild%20of%20India%20(EGI)%20and%20the%20Kolkata%20Press%20Club%20released%20statements%20addressing%20the%20arrest%20of%20a%20television%20journalist%20on%20duty%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20by%20the%20West%20Bengal%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EGI%20expressed%20its%20concern%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20describing%20the%20arrest%20of%20Santu%20Pan%2C%20a%20journalist%20with%20Republic%20Bangla%2C%20as%20%E2%80%9Cworrisome%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPan%2C%20who%20has%20been%20covering%20the%20incidents%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20for%20the%20channel%2C%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20during%20a%20live%20broadcast%20session%20on%20Monday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708438639000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20194058%2FJotoFet.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwest-bengal-opposition-leaders-reach-sandeshkhali%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20also%20registered%20surprise%20at%20the%20state%20police%E2%80%99s%20inability%20to%20apprehend%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Sheikh%20Shahjahan%2C%20who%20has%20been%20accused%20by%20Sandeshkhali's%20women%20of%20sexual%20assault.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwest-bengal-opposition-leaders-reach-sandeshkhali%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nawaz%20Sharif's%20party%20says%20Pakistan's%20electoral%20history%20not