20the%20pandemic%20subsided%2C%20more%20and%20more%20students%20began%20enrolling.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20students%20were%20amazed%20to%20see%20the%20transformation%20of%20the%20school.%20With%20water%2C%20proper%20lighting%2C%20painted%20walls%2C%20and%20a%20library%20awaiting%20them%2C%20word%20started%20to%20spread%2C%20and%20more%20students%20began%20to%20arrive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20with%20over%20100%20students%2C%20the%20school%20is%20teeming%20with%20creative%20minds.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20shift%20in%20parents%E2%80%99%20conversations%20and%20attitudes%20towards%20the%20school%20is%20striking.%20Now%2C%20they%20find%20it%20unusual%20if%20their%20children%20are%20at%20home%20during%20school%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20don%E2%80%99t%20wanna%20go%20home%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20the%20crackling%20sound%20of%20a%20bad%20network%20over%20the%20phone%20was%20the%20enthusiastic%20voice%20of%20a%20student%20studying%20in%20Class%2010%2C%20Shivani.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20clearly%20remember%20the%20old%20school.%20It%20was%20a%20school%20in%20name%20only.%20It%20did%20not%20have%20water%20or%20proper%20washrooms.%20But%20I%20love%20studying%20and%20did%20not%20want%20to%20miss%20out%20on%20it.%20But%20now%2C%20the%20school%20has%20changed%20completely.%20Gopal%20sir%20has%20always%20been%20a%20great%20teacher%2C%20but%20he%20is%20also%20a%20great%20person.%20The%20school%20now%20has%20water%20supply%2C%20mid-day%20meals%2C%20proper%20classrooms%20with%20beautifully%20painted%20walls%2C%20and%20also%20a%20library!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShivani%20says%20she%20loves%20to%20read%20and%20thoroughly%20enjoys%20the%20library.%3Cem%3E%20%E2%80%9CPehle%20school%20aane%20ka%20mann%20nahi%20hota%20tha%2C%20ab%20ghar%20jaane%20ka%20man%20nahi%20hota%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Earlier%2C%20I%20did%20not%20like%20coming%20to%20school