0his%20room%2C%20she%20saw%20Lalit%20hanging%20from%20the%20ceiling%20fan.%20My%20cousin%20has%20been%20a%20victim%20of%20caste-based%20oppression.%20When%20someone%20like%20Lalit%2C%20who%20comes%20from%20a%20poor%20Dalit%20family%2C%20excels%20in%20their%20career%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20go%20down%20well%20with%20people.%20He%20was%20subjected%20to%20mental%20torture.%20Lalit%20was%20an%20inspiration%20for%20the%20Dalit%20families%20in%20our%20village%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalit%20was%20the%20sole%20breadwinner%20of%20his%20family%2C%20which%20now%20stares%20at%20an%20uncertain%20future%2C%20Regar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20the%20family%20is%20demanding%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20and%20a%20government%20job%20for%20a%20family%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDalit%20rights%20activist%20Geegraj%20Jodli%2C%20along%20with%20local%20villagers%2C%20staged%20a%20dharna%20on%20February%2018%20in%20Neem%20Ka%20Thana%2C%20demanding%20justice%20for%20Lalit%2C%20whose%20last%20rites%20were%20conducted%20later%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Regar%20community%20is%20traditionally%20engaged%20in%20shoe%20making%20and%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20among%20the%20most%20marginalised%20Dalit%20communities.%20It%20is%20not%20easy%20for%20a%20youngster%20from%20such%20an%20underprivileged%20section%20of%20the%20society%20to%20enrol%20in%20the%20IIT%20or%20to%20appear%20for%20the%20UPSC.%20Lalit%E2%80%99s%20death%20shows%20us%20the%20cruel%20face%20of%20the%20feudalism%20ingrained%20in%20the%20society%20as%20he%20died%20because%20of%20caste%20oppression%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Neem%20Ka%20Thana-based%20activist%20Kailash%20Mina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmajoritarian-politics-and-the-plight-of-dalits%5C%22%3EMajoritarian%20Politics%20and%20the%20Plight%20of%20Dalits%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99ve%20been%20subjected%20to%20mental%20torture%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20alleged%20suicide%20note%20reportedly%20written%20by%20Lalit%2C%20it%20has%20been%20mentioned%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20clear%20the%20UPSC%20examination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20superintendent%20of%20police%20Rajendra%20Singh%2C%20circle%20officer%20Ajitgarh%2C%20and%20the%20investigating%20officer%20in%20the%20case%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20suicide%20note%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20forensic%20science%20laboratory%20(FSL)%20to%20confirm%20whether%20it%20has%20been%20written%20by%20Lalit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20an%20IIT%20graduate%20but%20while%20doing%20UPSC%2C%20I%20got%20trapped%20in%20this%20village%20development%20officer%20job%2C%20and%20now%20I%20am%20not%20able%20to%20do%20UPSC%20or%20anything%20else.%20Above%20all%20this%2C%20they%20pressurise%20me%20too%20much%20and%20nobody%20supports%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20alleged%20suicide%20note%20written%20in%20Hindi%20and%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20note%20mentioned%20several%20instances%20wherein%20Lalit%20was%20reportedly%20harassed%20in%20the%20course%20of%20his%20work.%20It%20said%20that%20BDO%20Ajitgarh%20pressurised%20him%20to%20register%20the%20corruption%20FIR%20against%20the%20sarpanch%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20not%20engaged%20in%20any%20corruption%2C%20not%20even%20a%20rupee%E2%80%99s%20worth%2C%20yet%20I%20was%20subjected%20to%20mental%20torture.%20Birbal%20ji%20(the%20father%20of%20the%20current%20sarpanch%20of%20Cheeplata)%20has%20created%20such%20a%20hostile%20environment%20in%20this%20panchayat%20that%20anyone%20wishing%20to%20work%20is%20unable%20to%20do%20so%2C%20and%20he%20has%20never%20allowed%20any%20work%20to%20progress%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EChaar%20mahine%20ho%20gaye%20mujhe%20depression%2C%20anxiety%20se%20jeete%20hue%2C%20ab%20nahin%20jeene.%20Sab%20jhuthe%20hain%20yaar%2C%20koi%20saath%20nahi%20deta.%20I%20am%20sorry%2C%20main%20haar%20gaya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(It%E2%80%99s%20been%20four%20months%20living%20with%20depression%20and%20anxiety%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20go%20on%20anymore%E2%80%A6%20Everybody%20is%20a%20liar.%20No%20one%20supports%20me.%20I%20am%20sorry%2C%20I%20have%20lost)%2C%E2%80%9D%20read%20the%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmental-health-caste%5C%22%3EWhen%20Mental%20Health%20Collides%20With%20Caste%20Identity%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFIR%20registered%20against%20sarpanch%2C%20his%20father%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Lalit%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20his%20relatives%20registered%20an%20FIR%20under%20Sections%20306%20(abetment%20of%20suicide)%20and%20120-B%20(criminal%20conspiracy)%20of%20the%20IPC%20and%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20SC%2FST%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act%2C%20on%20February%2018%20at%20the%20Thoi%20police%20station%20under%20Neem%20ka%20Thana%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeven%20accused%20persons%20have%20been%20named%20in%20the%20FIR%2C%20including%20Cheeplata%20sarpanch%20Manoj%20Gurjar%2C%20his%20father%20Birbal%20Ram%2C%20Narendra%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%20Jagdev%2C%20Pokhar%2C%20Panchayat%20Samiti%20BDO%2C%20and%20Mangal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20contacted%20Ajay%20Singh%20Nathawat%2C%20BDO%2C%20Ajitgarh%20Panchayat%20Samiti%2C%20who%20has%20been%20accused%20by%20Lalit%E2%80%99s%20family%20of%20pressuring%20him%20to%20register%20the%20corruption%20FIR%2C%20he%20denied%20the%20allegations%20but%20accepted%20that%20Lalit%20had%20met%20him%20on%20February%2015%20and%20expressed%20his%20desire%20to%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLalit%20had%20met%20me%20on%20February%2015%20and%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20resign.%20As%20the%20BDO%2C%20it%20is%20my%20duty%20to%20provide%20counselling%20to%20my%20staff%20and%20find%20out%20what%20is%20the%20reason.%20After%20I%20counseled%20him%2C%20he%20withdrew%20his%20resignation%20and%20I%20assured%20him%20I%20alone%20cannot%20take%20the%20decision%20of%20transferring%20him%20and%20told%20him%20that%20once%20the%20standing%20committee%20of%20the%20Panchayat%20Samiti%20meets%2C%20we%20will%20ensure%20that%20he%20is%20transferred%20to%20another%20gram%20panchayat.%20I%20promised%20him%20a%20solution%20by%20Monday.%20As%20for%20Lalit%20filing%20the%20corruption%20FIR%2C%20it%20is%20part%20of%20the%20general%20course%20of%20work%20of%20the%20village%20development%20officer%20to%20register%20FIRs%20in%20matters%20relating%20to%20corruption%20in%20gram%20panchayat%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nathawat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20that%20no%20persons%20have%20been%20arrested%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20family%20members%20of%20the%20deceased%20have%20alleged%20that%20Lalit%20died%20by%20suicide%20because%20ever%20since%20he%20had%20filed%20the%20corruption%20FIR%2C%20he%20was%20being%20threatened.%20Among%20those%20booked%20are%20the%20present%20sarpanch%20of%20Cheeplata%20and%20his%20father%2C%20who%20are%20accused%20of%20threatening%20the%20deceased.%20The%20BDO%20has%20also%20been%20booked%20in%20the%20FIR%20because%20Lalit%E2%80%99s%20relatives%20allege%20he%20pressured%20him%20to%20register%20the%20FIR.%20So%20far%2C%20no%20arrests%20have%20been%20made.%20We%20are%20investigating%20the%20matter.%20The%20family%20has%20given%20us%20an%20alleged%20suicide%20note%2C%20which%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20forensic%20lab%20to%20ascertain%20whether%20it%20was%20written%20by%20Lalit%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rajendra%20Singh%2C%20deputy%20superintendent%20of%20police%2C%20and%20circle%20officer%20Ajitgarh%2C%20who%20is%20the%20investigating%20officer%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3EIf%20you%20know%20someone%20%E2%80%93%20friend%20or%20family%20member%20%E2%80%93%20at%20risk%20of%20suicide%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20them.%20The%20Suicide%20Prevention%20India%20Foundation%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20tabindex%3D%5C%22-1%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.spif.in%2Fseek-help%2F%5C%22%20data-remove-tab-index%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.spif.in%2Fseek-help%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Emaintains%20a%20list%20of%20telephone%20numbers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%C2%A0they%20can%20call%20to%20speak%20in%20confidence.%20Icall%2C%20a%20counselling%20service%20run%20by%20TISS%2C%20has%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20tabindex%3D%5C%22-1%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fu%2F2%2Fd%2F1pzckT6ns2H1IlmwYwJa8EnBh_1u3gRA9cEOoA4zfilc%2Fedit%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0QhDXHgQodcWwJMkkAEw6eKfiwA4D7uBBktvHNmHcjBCmKBeSG2AYrd1Y%23gid%3D370032083%5C%22%20data-remove-tab-index%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20data-stringify-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fu%2F2%2Fd%2F1pzckT6ns2H1IlmwYwJa8EnBh_1u3gRA9cEOoA4zfilc%2Fedit%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0QhDXHgQodcWwJMkkAEw6eKfiwA4D7uBBktvHNmHcjBCmKBeSG2AYrd1Y%23gid%3D370032083%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Emaintained%20a%20crowdsourced%20list%20of%20therapists%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%20data-stringify-type%3D%5C%22italic%5C%22%3E%C2%A0across%20the%20country.%20You%20could%20also%20take%20them%20to%20the%20nearest%20hospital.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708435826000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20162409%2Fimage-1844.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frajasthan-dalit-govt-officer-dies-by-suicide-after-filing-corruption-case-against-sarpanch%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lalit%20Kumar%20Beniwal%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20village%20development%20officer%2C%20took%20his%20own%20life%20on%20February%2018%2C%20just%20three%20days%20after%20he%20had%20filed%20an%20FIR%20alleging%20corruption%20against%20the%20sarpanch%20of%20Cheeplata%20village%2C%20where%20he%20was%20stationed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frajasthan-dalit-govt-officer-dies-by-suicide-after-filing-corruption-case-against-sarpanch%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Startup%E2%80%99s%20Smart%20Stove%20Reduces%20Indoor%20Smoke%20by%2070%25%2C%20Saving%20Lives%20in%203%20Million%20Rural%20Homes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELalita%20Marshkole%E2%80%99s%20day%20would%20start%20promptly%20at%204%20am%20each%20morning%20as%20she%20prepared%20breakfast%20for%20her%20family%20of%20four.%20She%20devoted%20hours%20to%20cooking%20on%20the%20traditional%20mud%20%3Cem%3Echulha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(cooking%20stove)%20before%20packing%20lunch%20for%20her%20two%20children%20and%20heading%20off%20to%20work.%20After%20finishing%20work%2C%20she%20faced%20the%20challenging%20task%20of%20gathering%20firewood%20for%20cooking.%20She%20had%20to%20carry%20several%20kilograms%20of%20wood%20on%20her%20head%20as%20she%20made%20her%20way%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342261%2Fwoman-entrepreneur-saroj-prajapati-founder-moms-magic-pickle-mango-madhya-pradesh%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eback%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalita%20and%20her%20husband%20are%20both%20daily%20wage%20labourers%20in%20Badjhir%20village%2C%20located%20in%20the%20Seoni%20district%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ECentre%20for%20Science%20and%20Environment%20(CSE)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20nearly%20500%20million%20people%20in%20India%20lack%20access%20to%20clean%20cooking%20solutions.%20The%20report%20highlights%20that%2041%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%20%E2%80%94%20including%20individuals%20like%20Lalita%20%E2%80%94%20rely%20on%20biomass%20as%20cooking%20fuel.%20This%20reliance%20contributes%20to%20approximately%20340%20million%20tonnes%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20emissions%2C%20which%20accounts%20for%20nearly%2013%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20smoke%20from%20fuel%20burned%20for%20heating%20and%20cooking%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20contributors%20to%20indoor%20air%20pollution%20in%20India.%20The%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20estimates%20that%20every%20year%2C%203.2%20million%20people%20die%20prematurely%20from%20illnesses%20attributable%20to%20household%20air%20pollution%20caused%20by%20the%20incomplete%20combustion%20of%20solid%20fuels%20and%20kerosene%20used%20for%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20long-term%20solution%20for%20this%20is%20the%20usage%20of%20LPG%20stoves%2C%20which%20the%20Government%20is%20providing%20through%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%2C%20many%20are%20yet%20to%20adapt%20to%20it%20as%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20refills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ankit%20Mathur%20came%20across%20this%20problem%2C%20fresh%20out%20of%20IIM-Ahmedabad%2C%20in%202008%2C%20he%20started%20looking%20for%20a%20solution%20with%20his%20co-founder%20Neha%20Juneja.%20Interested%20in%20the%20sustainability%20space%2C%20they%20were%20working%20on%20renewable%20energy%20projects%20in%20rural%20areas.%20Here%2C%20they%20came%20face%20to%20face%20with%20the%20daily%20challenges%20in%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20saw%20that%20most%20of%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20time%20was%20spent%20either%20cooking%20or%20collecting%20firewood%20to%20cook.%20After%20observing%20the%20amount%20of%20smoke%20emanating%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3Echulhas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20studying%20its%20detrimental%20effects%20on%20health%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20work%20on%20a%20clean%20cooking%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20of%20research%20across%20various%20states%20and%20several%20prototypes%20later%2C%20they%20built%20the%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20a%20single-burner%2C%20high-efficiency%20cook%20stove%20that%20reduces%20smoke.%20Since%202012%2C%20Greenway%20Grameen%20Infra%20has%20sold%20three%20million%20cookstoves%20and%20wants%20to%20make%20clean%20cooking%20accessible%20to%20every%20part%20of%20rural%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProviding%20access%20to%20clean%20energy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-13-1708433713.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Greenway%20has%20provided%20clean%20energy%20to%20over%203%20million%20women%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-13-1708433713.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-13-1708433713-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-13-1708433713-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-13-1708433713-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-13-1708433713-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342462%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGreenway%20has%20provided%20clean%20energy%20to%20over%20three%20million%20women.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325587%2Fmumbai-entrepreneur-runs-lending-platform-for-rural-indian-women-loans-businesses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompleting%20his%20MBA%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20IIM-Ahmedabad%2C%20while%20most%20of%20his%20classmates%20were%20going%20for%20cushy%20corporate%20jobs%2C%20Ankit%20decided%20to%20walk%20off%20the%20beaten%20path.%20He%20contacted%20his%20Delhi%20College%20of%20Engineering%20classmate%2C%20Neha%20Juneja%2C%20and%20they%20decided%20to%20work%20in%20the%20sustainability%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20started%20by%20helping%20organisations%20effectively%20manage%20their%20carbon%20initiatives.%20During%20this%20time%2C%20they%20visited%20many%20villages%20and%20found%20that%20there%20weren%E2%80%99t%20many%20products%20addressing%20cleaner%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20that%20most%20households%20in%20the%20villages%20we%20visited%20were%20using%20rudimentary%20devices%20to%20cook.%20They%20were%20burning%20biomass%20to%20make%20their%20food.%20The%20energy%20efficiency%20of%20biomass%20is%20very%20low.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20you%20burn%201%2C000%20kilojoules%2C%20only%20one-tenth%20gets%20transferred%20to%20the%20cookstove%2C%20making%20it%20very%20wasteful%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20they%20resolved%20to%20develop%20an%20enhanced%20and%20environmentally%20friendly%20cookstove%20to%20alleviate%20the%20workload%20of%20women%20in%20rural%20regions.%20Beginning%20in%202010%2C%20Ankit%2C%20a%20mechanical%20engineer%2C%20and%20Neha%2C%20an%20industrial%20engineer%2C%20teamed%20up%20with%20Shoeb%20Kazi%2C%20a%20chemical%20engineer%2C%20to%20design%20an%20energy-efficient%20%E2%80%98smart%E2%80%99%20stove.%20The%20trio%20worked%20on%20building%20a%20prototype%2C%20conducting%20tests%2C%20and%20engaging%20in%20sales%20directly%20within%20villages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20a%20conscious%20decision%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ankit%2C%20about%20their%20stoves%20being%20priced%20at%20Rs%20500.%20They%20wanted%20to%20see%20how%20much%20people%20were%20willing%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20a%20major%20portion%20of%202010%20and%202011%2C%20they%20journeyed%20through%20over%2030%20villages%20spanning%2010%20districts%20across%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340464%2Fmadhopatti-uttar-pradesh-ias-factory-upsc-ips-irs-pcs-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Rajasthan.%20Over%20this%20time%2C%20they%20constructed%20more%20than%2010%20prototypes%20and%2C%20guided%20by%20consumer%20feedback%2C%20refined%20their%20design%20to%20arrive%20at%20the%20winning%20model%2C%20the%20Greenway%20Smart%20Stove.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20unique%20about%20the%20stove%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGreenway-Jumbo-stove-in-users-kitchen-min-1708434470-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20stove%20helps%20save%2065%20percent%20of%20fuel%20and%20reduces%20smoke%20by%2070%20percent.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGreenway-Jumbo-stove-in-users-kitchen-min-1708434470-scaled.jpg%202560w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGreenway-Jumbo-stove-in-users-kitchen-min-1708434470-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGreenway-Jumbo-stove-in-users-kitchen-min-1708434470-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGreenway-Jumbo-stove-in-users-kitchen-min-1708434470-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGreenway-Jumbo-stove-in-users-kitchen-min-1708434470-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGreenway-Jumbo-stove-in-users-kitchen-min-1708434470-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGreenway-Jumbo-stove-in-users-kitchen-min-1708434470-150x100.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FGreenway-Jumbo-stove-in-users-kitchen-min-1708434470-272x182.jpg%20272w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342474%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221706%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20stove%20helps%20save%2065%20percent%20of%20fuel%20and%20reduces%20smoke%20by%2070%20percent.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnkit%20explains%20that%20the%20Greenway%20Smart%20Stove%20comes%20with%20a%20patented%20air%20regulation%20technology%20that%20leads%20to%20better%20combustion%2C%20thereby%20increasing%20efficiency%20and%20reducing%20smoke.%20They%20have%20two%20models%3A%20the%20Smart%20Stove%20at%20Rs%202%2C199%2C%20and%20the%20Jumbo%20Stove%20at%20Rs%203%2C499%20for%20bigger%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stove%20has%20a%20single%20burner%20and%20works%20on%20different%20solid%20biomass%20fuels%2C%20such%20as%20wood%2C%20dry%20dung%2C%20crop%20waste%2C%20coconut%20waste%2C%20and%20bamboo.%20It%20reduces%20cooking%20time%20and%20is%20portable.%20The%20most%20important%20benefit%20of%20this%20stove%2C%20Ankit%20claims%2C%20is%20that%20it%20helps%20save%2065%20percent%20of%20fuel%20and%20reduces%20smoke%20by%2070%20percent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20product%20eliminates%20carbon%20monoxide%20from%20burning%20firewood.%20It%20reduces%20smoke%20emissions%2C%20making%20it%20safer%20for%20kitchen%20or%20household%20use.%20Unlike%20traditional%20%3Cem%3Echulhas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20often%20cause%20burns%2C%20this%20stove%20poses%20less%20risk%20of%20burns%20for%20women%20and%20children.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20reduces%20eye%20irritation%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Ankit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20environmental%20impact%20is%20concerned%2C%20Ankit%20states%20that%20each%20smart%20stove%20reduces%20greenhouse%20emissions%20by%20at%20least%20two%20tonnes%20per%20year.%20For%20the%20women%20using%20these%20stoves%2C%20besides%20the%20health%20aspect%2C%20their%20cooking%20time%20is%20greatly%20reduced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalita%2C%20who%20used%20to%20wake%20up%20at%204%20am%2C%20now%20rises%20at%205%20am%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20improved%20stove.%20She%20notes%20that%20cooking%20has%20become%20faster%20with%20the%20Smart%20stove%2C%20which%20she%20has%20been%20using%20for%20the%20past%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20stove%20involves%20much%20less%20cleaning%20as%20ash%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20fall%20on%20the%20floor.%20The%20firewood%20which%20we%20used%20to%20collect%20would%20last%20us%20for%20just%20two%20days%20earlier%2C%20now%20it%20lasts%20us%20for%2015%20to%2020%20days.%20Food%20is%20also%20made%20on%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20The%20time%20spent%20collecting%20firewood%20has%20also%20reduced%20greatly%2C%20leaving%20her%20with%20more%20time%20to%20spend%20with%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20customer%2C%20Geeta%20Rahangdale%2C%20says%20that%20it%20has%20made%20the%20kitchen%20cooler%20and%20uses%20very%20little%20firewood.%20She%20also%20appreciates%20the%20fact%20that%20food%20can%20be%20made%20anywhere%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProviding%20bargaining%20power%20to%20women%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FBjeJw_mFNAz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%2