08%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Flionel-messi-explains-hong-kong-no-show-in-video-to-fans-as-backlash-grows-13076108%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Flionel-messi-explains-hong-kong-no-show-in-video-to-fans-as-backlash-grows-13076108%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Economics%20of%20Coaching%20Classes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F19124917%2Fankita-konwar-zn9QqA-JTmY-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMarkets%20are%20acclaimed%20to%20give%20perfect%20solutions%20that%20satisfy%20both%20the%20consumer%20and%20the%20producer.%20They%20are%20said%20to%20bring%20together%20%E2%80%98all%20those%20who%20are%20willing%20and%20able%20to%20pay%E2%80%99%20with%20%E2%80%98all%20those%20who%20are%20willing%20and%20able%20to%20sell%E2%80%99%20at%20a%20certain%20price%20called%20the%20equilibrium%20price.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20situation%20of%20market%20equilibrium%2C%20that%20almost%20sounds%20platonic%2C%20several%20contentious%20questions%20emerge.%20Is%20everyone%20willing%20to%20pay%3F%20Who%20is%20not%20able%20to%20pay%3F%20Does%20it%20matter%3F%20Do%20they%20know%20what%20they%20are%20paying%20for%3F%20Who%20is%20the%20producer%3F%20Is%20profit%20their%20only%20motive%3F%20Obscure%20answers%20to%20these%20questions%20have%20led%20economists%20to%20conclude%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98invisible%20hand%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20market%20may%20not%20always%20be%20the%20best%20way%20to%20organise%20economic%20activity.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMarkets%20work%20efficiently%20for%20ordinary%20goods%20like%20online%20taxi%20services%20and%20even%20in%20case%20of%20%E2%80%98bads%E2%80%99%20such%20as%20tobacco%2C%20logical%20solutions%20are%20provided%20by%20the%20market.%20However%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98good%E2%80%99%20in%20question%20is%20education%20and%20the%20agents%20providing%20it%20are%20the%20coaching%20centres.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWithout%20getting%20into%20the%20philosophical%20debate%20on%20what%20is%20education%2C%20we%20look%20at%20this%20fairly%20complex%20good%20from%20an%20economist%E2%80%99s%20perspective%20and%20question%20the%20efficiency%20of%20coaching%20classes%20and%20how%20much%20well-being%20they%20actually%20produce%20in%20the%20society.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEducation%20in%20itself%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20school%20level%2C%20is%20declared%20to%20be%20a%20public%20good%20which%20is%20non-excludable%20and%20non-rival.%20This%20means%20that%20nobody%20should%20be%20excluded%20from%20its%20consumption%20and%20consumption%20by%20one%20should%20not%20rival%20the%20other%E2%80%99s.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20private%20schools%20occupying%2031.5%25%20of%20the%20total%20schools%2C%2046.7%25%20in%20total%20enrolments%20and%2049.3%25%20of%20total%20teachers%20in%20India%2C%20the%20%E2%80%98public%20good%E2%80%99%20nature%20of%20education%20becomes%20blurred.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrivate%20schooling%20is%20both%20excludable%20and%20rival.%20As%20if%20this%20complexity%20was%20not%20enough%2C%20shadow%20schooling%20in%20the%20form%20of%20coaching%20centres%20have%20mushroomed%20all%20over%20the%20country%20to%20meet%20an%20unprecedented%20demand.%20The%2075%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20round%20of%20the%20National%20Sample%20Survey%20(NSS%202017)%20states%20that%2027.2%25%20of%20students%20in%20rural%20areas%20and%2038.3%25%20of%20urban%20students%20take%20private%20tuitions%20at%20the%20secondary%20level.%20The%202022%20ASER%20report%20states%20that%20the%20proportion%20of%20rural%20Indian%20students%20between%20grades%201%20to%208%20taking%20private%20tuition%20classes%20increased%20from%2026.4%25%20in%202018%20to%2030.5%25%20in%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20genesis%20of%20a%20massive%20and%20progressively%20increasing%20demand%20for%20private%20coaching%20is%20the%20substandard%20state%20of%20government%20school%20education.%20Nearly%2035%25%20of%20both%20urban%20and%20rural%20students%20report%20this%20as%20the%20reason%20to%20opt%20for%20private%20schooling%2C%20according%20to%20NSSO%20data.%20The%20share%20of%20government%20schooling%20at%20all%20levels%20of%20schooling%20is%20higher%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20at%2068%25%20at%20the%20secondary%20and%20higher%20secondary%20level%3B%20than%20in%20urban%20areas%20where%20the%20same%20is%20at%2038.8%25%20explaining%20the%20increasing%20demand%20for%20private%20coaching.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20thriving%20coaching%20culture%20in%20urban%20and%20rural%20areas%20has%20emerged%20in%20a%20country%20that%E2%80%99s%20obsessed%20with%20entrance%20exams.%20Appearing%20as%20%E2%80%98ancillary%20units%E2%80%99%20of%20private%20schools%2C%20coaching%20centres%20have%20witnessed%20a%20phenomenal%20growth%20with%20some%20becoming%20unicorns%20and%20case%20studies%20at%20Harvard%20Business%20School.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20rising%20feeling%20of%20irrelevance%20of%20schools%20%E2%80%93%20since%20they%20do%20not%20provide%20the%20code%20to%20crack%20entrance%20exams%20%E2%80%93%20has%20made%20parents%20and%20students%20flock%20to%20private%20coaching%20centres%20to%20fill%20that%20gap.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20far%20what%20sounds%20like%20a%20simple%20story%20of%20effective%20demand%20in%20economics%20takes%20a%20twist%20because%20of%20the%20original%20nature%20of%20education%20as%20a%20public%20good%20that%20we%20began%20with.%20Public%20goods%20create%20%E2%80%98externalities%E2%80%99%20or%20spillover%20effects%20that%20affect%20the%20society%20positively%20apart%20from%20benefitting%20the%20consumers%20themselves.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEducation%2C%20justifiably%2C%20has%20several%20positive%20spillovers%20that%20may%20or%20may%20not%20recognised%20by%20an%20individual%20compelling%20the%20government%20to%20make%20basic%20schooling%20not%20only%20free%20but%20also%20compulsory.%20Occasionally%2C%20however%2C%20a%20public%20good%20can%20turn%20into%20a%20public%20bad%20when%20they%20give%20rise%20to%20negative%20externalities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrivate%20coaching%2C%20that%20was%20originally%20intended%20to%20compliment%20school%20education%20has%20almost%20become%20a%20%E2%80%98substitute%20good%E2%80%99%20with%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20private%20schools%20in%20the%20country%20that%20admit%20students%20without%20expecting%20them%20to%20be%20physically%20present.%20Emergence%20of%20coaching%20classes%20have%20turned%20mainstream%20schools%20into%20%E2%80%98dummy%E2%80%99%20schools%2C%20allowing%20students%20to%20only%20attend%20science%20practical%20classes%20and%20appear%20for%20exams.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20anticipated%20high%20rates%20of%20return%20through%20private%20coaching%20gives%20ground%20for%20the%20steep%20investment%20in%20it%2C%20overlooking%20several%20negative%20externalities%20that%20have%20been%20internalised%20by%20the%20stakeholders%20especially%20parents.%20Charging%20anywhere%20between%20Rs%201%2C000%20to%20Rs%206%2C000%20per%20hour%2C%20private%20coaching%20makes%20up%20for%20the%20third%20biggest%20component%20of%20household%20expenditure%20on%20education.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20fervent%20%E2%80%98neighbourhood%20effect%E2%80%99%20stating%20how%20consumer%20preferences%20are%20influenced%20by%20surroundings%2C%20seems%20to%20govern%20household%20decisions%20on%20consuming%20private%20coaching%20and%20with%20asymmetric%20information%20and%20uncertainty%2C%20in%20the%20form%20of%20lack%20of%20clear%20understanding%20of%20student%E2%80%99s%20own%20genuine%20interest%2C%20aptitude%20and%20inclination%20to%20pursue%20a%20certain%20course%20in%20future%2C%20it%20may%20result%20in%20suboptimal%20consumer%20choices.%20Massive%20advertising%20and%20aggressive%20marketing%20by%20coaching%20centres%20seems%20to%20have%20multiplied%20the%20demand%20for%20them%20validating%20the%20economic%20principle%20%E2%80%9CSupply%20creates%20its%20own%20demand%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0The%20externalities%20in%20case%20of%20private%20coaching%20are%20not%20immediately%20obvious%20as%20in%20a%20pollution%20emitting%20industry.%20The%20rise%20in%20dummy%20schools%2C%20extensive%20commercialisation%20of%20education%2C%20excessive%20focus%20on%20exams%20over%20actual%20learning%2C%20relentless%20scurrying%20of%20young%20children%20between%20school%20and%20coaching%20with%20little%20time%20for%20free%20play%20and%20finally%20increasing%20mental%20health%20issues%20among%20teenagers%20leading%20to%20growing%20suicide%20numbers%20are%20some%20of%20these%20problems.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Kota%2C%20the%20hub%20of%20private%20coaching%2C%20is%20infamous%20in%20reporting%2020-25%20cases%20of%20young%20students%20dying%20by%20suicide%20in%20fear%20of%20not%20fulfilling%20their%20parents%E2%80%99%20aspirations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStudents%20accounted%20for%208%25%20of%20the%20total%20deaths%20by%20suicide%20in%202022%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau.%20Of%20these%2C%20most%20of%20the%20students%20were%20in%20higher%20secondary%20school.%20This%20loss%20of%20potential%20human%20capital%20plus%20loss%20of%20productivity%20among%20related%20family%20members%20due%20to%20acute%20distress%20appear%20intangible%20although%20real.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProfessor%20Tilak%2C%20an%20eminent%20researcher%20in%20the%20field%20of%20education%20talks%20of%20three%20%E2%80%98fads%E2%80%99%20in%20education%3A%20Private%20education%20is%20most%20efficient%2C%20English-medium%20education%20is%20very%20important%20and%20pre-primary%20education%20is%20essential.%20Tilak%20argues%20that%20all%20these%20%E2%80%98fads%E2%80%99%20are%20mere%20views%20of%20people%20that%20lack%20research%20evidence.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%20private%20coaching%20is%20a%20sure%20road%20to%20success%20can%20be%20annexed%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98fads%E2%80%99%20list.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20IIT-Madras%20study%20revealed%20that%2050%25%20of%20students%20who%20got%20admission%20into%20IITs%20did%20not%20go%20to%20any%20coaching.%20The%20recent%20case%20of%20a%20missing%20teenager%20in%20Bangalore%2C%20who%20feared%20being%20reprimanded%20by%20parents%20for%20his%20poor%20performance%20in%20a%20coaching%20centre%2C%20created%20furore%20in%20society%2C%20prompting%20the%20government%20to%20introduce%20more%20regulation%20on%20private%20coaching.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECertainly%20government%20intervention%20is%20needed%20to%20correct%20%E2%80%98market%20failures%E2%80%99%3B%20in%20our%20case%20the%20failure%20of%20achieving%20welfare%20objectives%20intended%20through%20education.%20However%2C%20all%20regulation%20will%20be%20ineffective%20till%20the%20most%20important%20stakeholders%2C%20the%20parents%2C%20are%20fully%20convinced.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBetween%20the%20risk%20taken%20by%20parents%20while%20perceiving%20education%20as%20a%20capital%20good%20and%20the%20joy%20and%20satisfaction%20experienced%20by%20students%20who%20are%20consuming%20it%2C%20there%20are%20externalities%2C%20positive%20and%20negative.%20There%20is%20a%20need%20to%20recognize%20and%20educate%20that%20education%20is%20a%20good%20where%20the%20impact%20is%20on%20parents%20(through%20fees)%2C%20incidence%20in%20on%20students%20(through%20their%20schooling%20experience)%20and%20the%20effects%20are%20on%20the%20society%20(that%20could%20be%20positive%20or%20negative).%20Well-informed%20choices%20of%20parents%2C%20in%20clear%20recognition%20of%20their%20children%E2%80%99s%20interests%20and%20abilities%20will%20alone%20bring%20about%20the%20desired%20outcomes%20benefitting%20individually%20and%20collectively.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDr%20Pushkarni%20Panchamukhi%20is%20associate%20dean%20at%20School%20of%20Economics%2C%20RV%20University%2C%20Bangalore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708426805000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F19124917%2Fankita-konwar-zn9QqA-JTmY-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fthe-economics-of-coaching-classes%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20thriving%20coaching%20culture%20in%20both%20urban%20and%20rural%20areas%20has%20emerged%20in%20a%20country%20that's%20obsessed%20with%20entrance%20exams.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fthe-economics-of-coaching-classes%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20denies%20claims%20that%20Alexei%20Navalny%20was%20poisoned%20with%20novichok%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708425540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-alexei-navalny-vladimir-putin_6457936.jpg%3F20240216151055%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Falexei-navalny-russia-denies-claims-that-putin-critic-was-poisoned-with-novichok-13076085%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia%20has%20denied%20claims%20made%20by%20Alexei%20Navalny's%20widow%20that%20he%20was%20poisoned%20by%20the%20nerve%20agent%20novichok.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A215%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Falexei-navalny-russia-denies-claims-that-putin-critic-was-poisoned-with-novichok-13076085%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Falexei-navalny-russia-denies-claims-that-putin-critic-