%20and%20whose%20offerings%20he%20accepted.%20The%20randomisation%20seems%20to%20have%20added%20to%20his%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmma%20once%20asked%20me%20to%20take%20her%20to%20the%20ashram%20that%20had%20grown%20around%20the%20Paramhansa.%20She%20stopped%20when%20we%20reached%20a%20point%20from%20where%20we%20could%20see%20the%20saint.%20I%20had%20assumed%20that%20she%20would%20want%20to%20spend%20some%20time%20in%20the%20ashram.%20Before%20I%20could%20ask%2C%20she%20explained%20that%20we%20should%20not%20disturb%20saints%20as%20they%20are%20always%20immersed%20in%20meditation.%20We%20left%20a%20few%20minutes%20later.%20This%20was%20the%20first%20and%20last%20time%20I%20had%20a%20%3Cem%3Edarshan%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20a%20Paramhansa%2C%20even%20if%20from%20a%20distance.%20But%20we%20had%20grown%20up%20hearing%20tales%20of%20Paramhansas%20and%20other%20saints%20who%20dwelled%20in%20our%20district%20and%20the%20neighbouring%20Gwalior%20during%20the%20early%2020th%20century.%20Our%20menfolk%20had%20served%20the%20princely%20state%20in%20various%20capacities%20and%20treated%20the%20village%20with%20all%20kinds%20of%20tales%20from%20there%2C%20including%20the%20ones%20featuring%20Paramhansas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20fixed%20points%20of%20a%20Paramhansa%20tale%20included%20his%20(always%20a%20male)%20dramatic%20spiritual%20transformation%20(leaving%20us%20wondering%20why%20similar%20encounters%20did%20not%20awaken%20us)%20and%20the%20idiosyncrasies%20that%20set%20him%20apart%20from%20other%20saints.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20Paramhansas%2C%20there%20were%20other%20saintly%20figures.%20Khatkhata%20Baba%2C%20a%20bureaucrat%20turned%20ascetic.%20Dinanath%20Baba%2C%20a%20soldier%20turned%20ascetic.%20A%20gentle%20Mahamandaleshwar%20who%20paid%20a%20visit%20to%20our%20village.%20An%20enigmatic%20fakir%20who%20occasionally%20visited%20the%20village%20but%20disappeared%20after%20curing%20a%20child%20of%20chronic%20knee%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressive%20Parshuramas%20complemented%20reticent%20Paramhansas%20in%20this%20world.%20Ramlila%20was%20a%20major%20cultural%20event%20and%20%3Cem%3EParshurami%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20among%20its%20highlights.%20Parshuramas%20were%20groomed%20in%20%3Cem%3Eakharas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20where%20both%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20were%20teachers.%20When%20Parshurama%20entered%20Raja%20Janaka%E2%80%99s%20assembly%20during%20Sita%20Svyamvar%20he%20supposedly%20thundered%20and%20stomped.%20The%20stage%20ought%20to%20creak%20when%20a%20credible%20Parshurama%20stomps.%20It%20is%20easy%20to%20understand%20why%20only%20wrestlers%20would%20fit%20this%20role%2C%20but%20they%20were%20also%20expected%20to%20cultivate%20an%20interest%20in%20Tulsi%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20would%20laugh%20remembering%20how%20an%20itinerant%20Parshurama%20was%20embarrassed%20when%20he%20kept%20stomping%2C%20but%20the%20stage%20stood%20like%20a%20rock%20because%20it%20was%20built%20using%20the%20%3Cem%3Etakht%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20such%20and%20such%20person.%20That%20%3Cem%3Etakht%3C%2Fem%3E%20acquired%20an%20aura%20of%20its%20own%20and%20remained%20unbeatable%20over%20the%20years.%20The%20daily%20routine%20of%20those%20devoted%20to%20wrestling%20and%20their%20successes%20was%20recalled%20in%20great%20detail.%20Children%20would%20hear%20with%20both%20amazement%20and%20irritation%20how%20wrestlers%20drank%20buckets%20full%20of%20milk%20in%20the%20morning.%20Some%20even%20had%20a%20buffalo%20to%20themselves%20and%20allegedly%20drank%20milk%20until%20it%20flowed%20out%20of%20their%20nostrils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamlila%2C%20Ramayana%20path%2C%20and%20Bhagvata%20path%20were%20also%20occasions%20for%20collective%20deliberation%20on%20finer%20points%20of%20literature%20and%20life.%20Many%20of%20the%20celebrated%20participants%20in%20these%20conversations%20had%20learnt%20the%20texts%20such%20as%20Ramacharitmanas%20just%20by%20virtue%20of%20having%20sat%20through%20recitations%20since%20childhood.%20These%20non-literate%20savants%20would%20spend%20whole%20nights%20debating%20a%20couplet%20or%20two.%20(Their%20college-educated%20grandchildren%20struggle%20to%20string%20together%20140%20characters.)%20Stories%20told%20and%20debated%20in%20these%20gatherings%20became%20part%20of%20the%20collective%20wisdom%20of%20the%20village%20and%20it%20turned%20to%20them%20in%20case%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Edharma%20sankat%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20stories%20were%20built%20around%20spiritual%20or%20mythological%20characters%20though.%20Feasts%20were%20another%20highlight%20of%20village%20life.%20Voracious%20eaters%2C%20generous%20hosts%20and%20great%20cooks%20were%20heroes%20of%20many%20a%20story.%20A%20host%20locked%20up%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebaaraat%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20his%20large%20compound%20and%20fed%20them%20over%20several%20days%20until%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20eat%20anymore.%20A%20gentleman%20with%20a%20voracious%20appetite%20could%20be%20satisfied%20by%20only%20two%20households%20in%20the%20entire%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20village%20was%20in%20turn%20nested%20in%20a%20larger%20universe%20that%20included%20other%20neighbouring%20villages%20that%20belonged%20to%20%3Cem%3Ebrothers%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20who%20partook%20in%20our%20stories%20and%20contributed%20to%20our%20pool%20of%20stories.%20These%20villages%20shared%20a%20three-tiered%20origin%20myth%20beginning%20with%20their%20displacement%20a%20millennium%20ago%20from%20a%20distant%20land%20in%20the%20wider%20%3Cem%3EBraj%3C%2Fem%3E%20region%20culminating%20in%20their%20eventual%20settlement%20at%20their%20respective%20present%20sites%20before%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20British.%20The%20village%20was%20also%20bound%20through%20marriage%20to%20a%20wider%20network%20of%20villages%20around%20the%20Yamuna%20and%20its%20tributaries%20that%20further%20enriched%20the%20pool%20of%20stories.%20Occasionally%2C%20influences%20from%20beyond%20intersected%20this%20universe.%20Swami%20Dayanand%20Saraswati%20paid%20a%20visit%20to%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebrother%3C%2Fem%3E%20village%E2%80%99s%20titular%20family%20whose%20path%20later%20also%20crossed%20that%20of%20Motilal%20Nehru.%20Stories%20for%20another%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20stories%20are%20our%20(lived%20and)%20remembered%20world.%20Even%20those%20of%20us%20who%20were%20born%20and%20brought%20up%20in%20distant%20towns%20belonged%20to%20this%20world%20because%20they%20were%20raised%20on%20a%20regular%20diet%20of%20these%20stories.%20The%20stories%20served%20as%20the%20bedrock%20of%20our%20faith%20that%20otherwise%20did%20not%20have%20visible%20anchors%20as%20there%20has%20never%20been%20a%20temple%20%3Cem%3Ewithin%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20village.%20(A%20century%20or%20two%20old%20%3Cem%3Echabutra%2Fplatform%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20village%20though%20has%20retained%20an%20assortment%20of%20small%20unrecognisable%20fragments%20of%20a%20medieval%20Hindu%20or%20Jain%20temple.%20Also%2C%20there%20are%20two%20minimalist%20platforms%20dedicated%20to%20Hanuman%20%3Cem%3Eoutside%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20village.)%20The%20hearth%20and%20tulsi%20at%20home%2C%20a%20banyan%20in%20the%20village%20and%20a%20peepal%20in%20the%20fields%20served%20as%20our%20axis%20mundi%2C%20with%20the%20world%20of%20stories%20wrapped%20around%20them%20like%20amma%E2%80%99s%20cotton%20saree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F11100219%2FScreenshot-2022-07-11-at-10.02.04-AM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221107%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F11100219%2FScreenshot-2022-07-11-at-10.02.04-AM.png%201107w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F11100219%2FScreenshot-2022-07-11-at-10.02.04-AM-300x166.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F11100219%2FScreenshot-2022-07-11-at-10.02.04-AM-1024x568.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-606843%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22614%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20LivinTheDream%2FFlickr%20(CC%20BY%202.0)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20newer%20urban%20homes%2C%20each%20of%20us%20populated%20the%20space%20around%20our%20axis%20mundi%20with%20seemingly%20unconnected%20things.%20A%20dargah%20in%20Nagore%20and%20a%20church%20in%20Trivandrum%2C%20the%20grand%20Srirangam%20and%20a%20barely%20noticed%20roadside%20temple%20in%20Old%20Delhi%2C%20a%20Gupta%20temple%20in%20Lalitpur%20and%20a%20village%20deity%20in%20Jaisalmer%2C%20a%20ziarat%20in%20Budgam%20and%20an%20asthan%20in%20Sopore%2C%20a%20monastery%20in%20Leh%20and%20a%20Gurdwara%20in%20Kargil%2C%20sacred%20trees%20in%20Senapati%20and%20Niuland%2C%20a%20courtyard%20of%20a%20goddess%20in%20Srinagar%20and%20a%20church%20in%20Pungro.%20All%20these%20and%20much%20more%20fit%20in%20effortlessly%20in%20the%20small%20but%20capacious%20world%20conjured%20by%20rustic%20storytellers%2C%20who%20had%20not%20heard%20of%20most%20of%20these%20places.%20The%20world%20they%20built%20is%20like%20our%20puja%20ghars%20where%2033%20crore%20gods%20and%20memorabilia%20from%20their%20tirthas%20quietly%20squeeze%20in%20without%20complaints.%20It%20is%20like%20Amma%E2%80%99s%20tiny%20cot%20that%20accommodated%20the%20five%20of%20us.%20In%20that%20matchbox-sized%20space%2C%20time%20stood%20still%20in%20the%20punishing%20summers%20of%20the%20north.%20There%20she%20wove%20bizarre%20tales%20of%20epic%20proportions%20spanning%20ages%20and%20universes%2C%20featuring%20gods%2C%20ghosts%2C%20and%20gentlemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20storytellers%20built%20a%20world%20with%20a%20small%20number%20of%20mostly%20implausible%20tales%2C%20which%20were%20told%20and%20retold%20innumerable%20times%20till%20no%20one%20knew%20or%20cared%20what%20the%20original%20or%20the%20origin%20was.%20It%20was%20often%20not%20clear%20if%20the%20storytellers%20used%20local%20tales%20to%20fill%20in%20the%20gaps%20in%20Ramayana%20and%20Mahabharata%20or%20used%20the%20latter%20to%20fill%20in%20the%20gaps%20in%20the%20local%20tales.%20In%20any%20case%2C%20the%20world%20of%20stories%20we%20inherited%20easily%20accommodates%20both%20the%20unknown%20and%20the%20unknowable.%20And%20it%20is%20to%20this%20world%20that%20we%20turn%20to%20when%20we%20find%20ourselves%20in%20times%20of%20trouble.%20These%20shared%20stories%20are%20the%20means%20through%20which%20we%20understand%20ourselves%20and%20the%20world%20around%20us.%20Until%20a%20decade%20or%20two%20ago%2C%20outsiders%20understood%20us%20as%20the%20sum%20of%20our%20personal%20idiosyncrasies%20and%20the%20stories%20told%20in%20and%20about%20our%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bedrock%20of%20our%20faith%2C%20these%20stories%20survived%20the%20last%20century.%20But%2C%20perhaps%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20ages%2C%20the%20older%20generation%20has%20begun%20to%20forget%20the%20stories%20even%20before%20having%20been%20able%20to%20groom%20storytellers%20among%20their%20grandchildren%2C%20who%20have%20been%20claimed%20by%20urban%20dreams%20sustained%20on%20maddening%20inputs%20of%20men%20and%20material.%20Completely%20oblivious%20of%20the%20enormous%20cultural%20loss%20and%20ill-equipped%20to%20imagine%20alternatives%2C%20the%20grandchildren%20are%20adrift%20and%20clutch%20at%20whatever%20comes%20their%20way%20or%20is%20hurled%20at%20them%20%E2%80%93%20imagined%20nations%2C%20enumerated%20faiths%2C%20purported%20mother%20tongues%20and%20careerism-cum-consumerism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EVikas%20Kumar%20teaches%20economics%20at%20Azim%20Premji%20University%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20is%20the%20author%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cambridge.org%2Fcore%2Fbooks%2Fnumbers-as-political-allies%2F4FB6F90A77F38501629062AA2DD4DA1C%5C%22%3ENumbers%20as%20Political%20Allies%3A%20T