ssange-in-last-ditch-legal-bid-against-extradition-to-us%2Famp_articleshow%2F107851334.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fassange-in-last-ditch-legal-bid-against-extradition-to-us%2Famp_articleshow%2F107851334.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmers%20at%20the%20Haryana%20Border%3A%20The%20Chronology%20of%20How%20We%20Got%20Here%20Again%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F20142850%2FScreenshot-2024-02-20-at-2.28.12.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20silent%20period%20of%20gestation%2C%20the%20Indian%20farmers%20movement%20has%20rejuvenated%20itself.%C2%A0%20Recently%2C%20some%20farmers%E2%80%99%20group%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20the%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(SKM)%20%E2%80%93%20a%20faction%20which%20is%20un-afilliated%20to%20any%20political%20party%20%E2%80%93%20launched%20a%20peaceful%20convoy%20of%20thousands%20of%20tractors-trolleys%20to%20New%20Delhi.%20The%20convoy%20was%20stopped%20on%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20border%20at%20Shambhu%20and%20the%20farmers%20were%20met%20with%20brutal%20state%20violence%20as%20they%20tried%20to%20cross%20over%20into%20Haryana.%20The%20tractorcade%20was%20to%20reach%20Delhi%20on%20February%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20of%20police%20drones%20dropping%20tear%20gas%20bombs%2C%20and%20of%20cops%20using%20rubber%20pellets%20and%20batons%20have%20emerged%2C%20signalling%20the%20deep%20hostility%20of%20the%20government%20towards%20the%20peaceful%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movement.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20farmers%20unions%20and%20its%20allies%20declared%20a%20Grameen%20Bharat%20Bandh%20(Rural%20India%20general%20strike)%20on%20February%2016.%20Various%20workers%E2%80%99%20unions%20supported%20the%20call%20and%20called%20for%20an%20industry%20strike%20too.%20They%20blocked%20roads%20and%20highways%20in%20civil%20disobedience%20against%20the%20unprovoked%20state%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20the%20farmers%20deserve%20this%20treatment%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20weren%E2%80%99t%20they%20allowed%20to%20exercise%20their%20fundamental%20right%20to%20protest%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20did%20things%20get%20so%20bad%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20look%20at%20the%20chronology%20of%20events%20that%20led%20to%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20peaceful%20convoy%20and%20the%20blockading%20of%20roads%20with%20barbed%20wire%2C%20spikes%20and%20concrete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202021%2C%20the%20farmers%20decided%20to%20return%20home%20after%20the%20three%20farm%20laws%20they%20had%20protested%20against%20for%20nearly%20two%20years%20were%20rescinded.%20They%20left%20in%20good%20faith%2C%20as%20the%20Modi%20government%20promised%20them%20that%20their%20other%20demands%20%E2%80%93%20like%20a%20law%20on%20minimum%20support%20price%2C%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20cases%2C%20compensation%20for%20the%20farmers%20who%20died%20during%20the%20protest%2C%20etc.%20would%20be%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20continued%20its%20dialogue%20with%20the%20SKM%20until%20January%202022%2C%20when%20a%20statement%20on%20MSP%20was%20made.%20After%20that%2C%20all%20talks%20stopped.%20Their%20camps%20unpegged%20from%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20borders%2C%20the%20SKM%20knew%20the%20farmers%20and%20their%20movement%20had%20lost%20their%20leverage.%20This%20is%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20trust%20gap%20between%20the%20government%20and%20SKM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20the%20government%20also%20created%20a%20committee%20to%20further%20deliberate%20on%20the%20MSP%20question.%20From%20the%20start%2C%20the%20committee%20was%20boycotted%20by%20SKM%20because%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1028588%2Fsamyukt-kisan-morcha-rejects-centres-msp-panel-says-it-includes-leaders-who-supported-farm-laws%5C%22%3Eof%20the%20clear%20bias%20in%20its%20composition%3C%2Fa%3E.%20An%20independent%20member%20even%20resigned%20from%20the%20committee%2C%20adding%20more%20weight%20to%20the%20farmers%20cause.%20This%20was%20the%20second%20betrayal%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20government%20refused%20to%20talk%20with%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20leadership%2C%20the%20SKM%20used%20the%20next%20two%20years%20to%20build%20the%20campaign%20around%20India%20for%20MSP%20and%20also%20lent%20its%20support%20to%20other%20agrarian%20and%20social%20causes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20it%20came%20to%20light%20that%20certain%20government-backed%20farmers%20union%20had%20started%20to%20emerge%20and%20even%20successful%20attempts%20were%20made%20to%20break%20bigger%20farmers%E2%80%99%20unions%20like%20Bhartiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Ugraha)%20and%20BKU%20(Tikait).%20As%20farmers%20were%20trying%20to%20gain%20ground%20around%20the%20country%2C%20attempts%20were%20being%20made%20to%20weaken%20them%20at%20home.%20This%20increased%20the%20trust%20gap.%20Yet%20the%20SKM%20pulled%20through%20and%20reorganised%20itself%20in%20a%20stronger%20fashion%2C%20rebuilding%20its%20cadre%2C%20purging%20members%20and%20reorganising%20itself%20for%20future%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20six%20months%2C%20farmer%20groups%20have%20been%20organising%20all%20over%20India%20to%20reiterate%20the%20demand%20for%20MSP%20and%20other%20agrarian%20issues.%20A%20new%20coalition%20was%20emerging%20between%20the%20north%20and%20south.%20But%20the%20first%20sparks%20were%20seen%20in%20Punjab%20again%2C%20when%20farmers%20launched%20sit-ins%20and%20hunger%20strikes%20for%20MSP.%20They%20approached%20the%20Modi%20government%20again%20for%20talks.%20As%20a%20reaction%20to%20this%20new%20wave%2C%20the%20government%20blocked%20Twitter%20accounts%2C%20and%20started%20arresting%20and%20weakening%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20the%20unions%20continued.%20Even%20before%20the%20convoy%20started%2C%20some%20of%20the%20farmers%20leaders%20met%20with%20Central%20ministers%20to%20remind%20the%20government%20of%20its%20promises%20and%20informed%20them%20of%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20resolve%20to%20head%20to%20Delhi%20for%20a%20peaceful%20protest.%20After%20which%20and%20even%20now%2C%20all%20talks%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarmers%E2%80%99%20demands%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20demands%2C%20nothing%20has%20changed.%20They%20have%20had%20the%20same%20demands%20since%20they%20left%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20borders.%20The%20demands%20include%20implementing%20a%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20for%20crops%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20Swaminathan%20formula%2C%20ensuring%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20of%20procurement%2C%20providing%20debt%20waivers%2C%20refraining%20from%20increasing%20electricity%20tariffs%20or%20implementing%20smart%20meters.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20seek%20free%20allocation%20of%20300%20units%20of%20power%20for%20farming%2C%20domestic%20use%2C%20and%20shops%2C%20comprehensive%20crop%20insurance%2C%20and%20increasing%20pensions%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20proposal%20for%20five-year%20support%20of%20five%20crops%20does%20not%20cut%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20simple%20words%2C%20what%20the%20farmers%20want%20is%20a%20fair%20price%20for%20their%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20question%20now%20is%20will%20the%20Modi%20government%20give%20in%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndra%20Shekhar%20Singh%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eis%20an%20independent%20agri-policy%20analyst%20and%20writer.%20He%20was%20the%20former%20director%2C%20policy%20and%20outreach%2C%20at%20NSAI.%20He%20also%20hosts%20The%20Wire%E2%80%99s%20agriculture%20talk%20show%2C%20Krishi%20ki%20baat%2FFarm%20Talks.%20He%20tweets%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Findrassingh%5C%22%3E%40indrassingh%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%