r%20were%20taken%20care%20of%20by%20the%20state%20by%20ensuring%20a%20steady%20flow%20of%20grains%20and%20bread.%20Bread%20placated%20the%20public%20and%20kept%20their%20basic%20needs%20fulfilled%2C%20while%20the%20circus%20ensured%20that%20they%20were%20distracted%20from%20the%20dismal%20state%20of%20affairs%20around%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20utilise%20American%20journalist%20Alice%20Schroeder%E2%80%99s%20succinct%20and%20useful%20explanations%20of%20what%20the%20Roman%20system%20of%20bread%20and%20circus%20meant%20as%20a%20framework%20to%20make%20my%20case%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20While%20we%20are%20in%20the%20times%20of%20focusing%20on%20Ram%20Rajya%2C%20let%20us%20compare%20our%20current%20state%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ERoman%20Rajya%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERome%20in%20the%20first%20two%20centuries%20A.D.%20faced%20a%20yawning%20gulf%20between%20rich%20and%20poor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20we%20chest%20thump%20our%20way%20to%20being%20the%203rd%20largest%20economy%20globally%2C%20we%20are%20facing%20an%20ever-widening%20gap%20between%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20poor.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20Indian%20businessmen%20and%20industrialists%20are%20climbing%20up%20on%20the%20global%20billionaire%20index%20while%20on%20the%20other%2C%20self-employed%20wages%20and%20regular%20wages%20have%20seen%20a%20negligible%20increase%20since%202017.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20has%20obfuscated%20this%20truth%20by%20clutching%20on%20to%20NITI%20Aayog%E2%80%99s%20Multi-Dimensional%20Poverty%20Index%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1996271%23%3A~%3Atext%3DNITI%2520Aayog-%2C24.82%2520crore%2520Indians%2520escape%2520Multidimensional%2520Poverty%2520in%2520last%25209%2520years%2Cshow%2520significant%2520signs%2520of%2520improvement.%5C%22%3Ewhich%20claims%20that%2025%20million%20individuals%20have%20been%20lifted%20out%20of%20poverty%20in%20the%20past%209%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Without%20any%20information%20on%20household%20consumption%20and%20savings%2C%20the%20government%20has%20hidden%20income-based%20indicators%20of%20poverty%20and%20is%20relying%20on%20this%20flawed%2C%20inaccurate%20and%20cherry-picked%20statistic.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmake-in-india-10-years-government-silence%5C%22%3EAs%20%E2%80%98Make%20in%20India%E2%80%99%20Enters%2010th%20Year%2C%20What%20Does%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Silence%20Mean%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIts%20economy%20created%20few%20exportable%20goods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20drama%20and%20circus%20of%20investor%20summits%20and%20MoUs%20under%20Make%20in%20India%2C%20manufacturing%20has%20not%20picked%20up%20in%20India.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20growth%20rate%20of%20the%20manufacturing%20sector%20has%20averaged%205.9%25%20since%202013-14%2C%20the%20share%20of%20manufacturing%20has%20remained%20stagnant%20and%20was%20at%2016.4%25%20in%202022-23%2C%20and%20in%20fact%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fpolicy%2Feconomy-make-in-india-half-of-manufacturing-jobs-lost-in-five-years-2256758%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFrom%2520employing%252051%2520million%2520people%2Ccrisis%2520caused%2520by%2520the%2520pandemic.%5C%22%3Emanufacturing%20jobs%20halved%20between%202016%20and%202021%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManufacturing%20has%20reached%20historical%20lows%20under%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20government%20(BJP).%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Flead%2Fat-the-root-of-indias-manufacturing-challenge%2Farticle66920771.ece%5C%22%3EIn%202022-23%20it%20grew%20a%20dismal%201.3%25%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20the%20second-lowest%20growth%20in%20the%20last%2025%20years.%20The%20only%20year%20worse%20than%20this%20was%202019-20%2C%20when%20the%20output%20declined%20by%203%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20focus%20is%20on%20the%20optics%20of%20being%20a%20manufacturing%20giant%20of%20smartphones%2C%20yet%20the%20devil%20is%20in%20the%20details.%20Wherein%2C%20government%20schemes%20have%20incentivised%20the%20exporting%20of%20phones%20from%20India%2C%20while%20ignoring%20incentivising%20value%20addition.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Caesars%20created%20make-work%20and%20part-time%20jobs%2C%20subsidised%20housing%20and%20doled%20out%20grain.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20assembly%20elections%20in%202023%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20announced%20the%20extension%20of%20the%20pandemic-induced%20free%20food-grains%20scheme%20to%20800%20million%20Indians%20for%20another%205%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20This%20implies%20that%20nearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fin-another-sign-of-deep-economic-distress-modi-says-free-ration-to-800-million-to-continue%5C%22%3Ea%20third%20of%20the%20Indian%20population%20needs%20government-guaranteed%20food%20for%20their%20survival.%3C%2Fa%3E%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20increase%20in%20demand%20for%20MGNREGA%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhich%20was%20once%20critiqued%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0indicates%20burgeoning%20economic%20distress.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20bear%20the%20burden%20of%20social%20security%20and%20benefits%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%20led%20to%20them%20cancelling%20full-time%20recruitment%20and%20instead%20introducing%20a%20part-time%20employment%20option.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20drama%20was%20not%20far%20behind%20as%20the%20naming%20of%20the%20scheme%20was%20Bollywood-influenced%20Agnipath%20and%20Agniveer.%20Subsidised%20housing%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20push%20of%20this%20government%20with%20renewed%20and%20consistent%20allocations%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fpm-awas-yojana-problems%5C%22%3Edespite%20significant%20failures%20of%20the%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20indeed%2C%20we%20were%20a%20thriving%20economy%2C%20successfully%20eradicating%20poverty%2C%20why%20do%20we%20need%20to%20extend%20government%20spending%20on%20basic%20needs%3F%20Probably%2C%20since%20these%20insecurities%20in%20times%20of%20increasing%20inflation%20and%20stagnating%20wages%2C%20are%20a%20Roman%20recipe%20for%20political%20risk%20to%20the%20ruling%20regime.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20emperors%20added%20holidays%20until%2C%20eventually%2C%20the%20Romans%20spent%20half%20their%20days%20attending%20gladiator%20games%2C%20public%20executions%20and%20chariot%20races.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUntil%20January%2022%2C%202024%2C%20holidays%20for%20religious%20festivals%20and%20national%20holidays%20remained%20differentiated.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20marked%20the%20culmination%20of%20the%20union%20of%20the%20religion%20and%20the%20state.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESteeped%20in%20religious%20fervour%2C%20banks%2C%20schools%2C%20government%20offices%20and%20institutions%20declared%20shortened%20work%20hours%20or%20holidays%20to%20celebrate%20this%20epochal%20moment.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20while%20the%20government%20failed%20to%20ensure%20medical%20support%20and%20essential%20items%20to%20the%20general%20public%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20we%20had%20a%20variety%20of%20circuses%20to%20distract%20us.%20From%20the%20media%20circus%20focused%20on%20a%20Bollywood%20actor%E2%80%99s%20unfortunate%20death%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20an%20alleged%20attempt%20to%20destabilise%20the%20country%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20by%20the%20o