after%20parting%20ways%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20claimed%20that%20the%20NC%20was%20%E2%80%9Cseeking%20time%E2%80%9D%20to%20meet%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20central%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20seeking%20time%20(for%20the%20meeting)%20at%2011%20or%2012%20at%20night.%20Why%20so%3F%20Why%20not%20during%20daytime%3F%20It%20looks%20suspicious%2C%E2%80%9D%20Azad%20told%20the%20TV%20channel%2C%20without%20taking%20any%20names.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20reporter%20suggested%20that%20the%20NC%20leaders%20were%20seeking%20an%20appointment%20with%20Modi%20and%20Shah%2C%20Azad%20replied%3A%20%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20just%20say%20central%20leaders.%20Why%20are%20you%20saying%20it%20so%20openly.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzad%20also%20criticised%20the%20NC%20president%20for%20his%20alleged%20doublespeak%20while%20accusing%20him%20of%20using%20religion%20for%20political%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNobody%20is%20more%20secular%20than%20me%20in%20India.%20But%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20temples%20to%20appease%20the%20Hindu%20voters.%20I%20won%E2%80%99t%20abuse%20India%20or%20Hindus%20to%20garner%20the%20votes%20of%20Muslims%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Azad%2C%20in%20a%20veiled%20dig%20at%20the%20senior%20Abdullah%20whose%20video%20clips%20singing%20Hindi%20bhajans%20are%20popular%20on%20social%20media%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DPAP%20president%2C%20who%20was%20awarded%20Padma%20Bhushan%20in%202022%2C%20is%20the%20only%20senior%20politician%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20who%20has%20been%20allowed%20to%20retain%20his%20ministerial%20bungalow%20after%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20was%20downgraded%20into%20a%20union%20territory%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzad%20was%20also%20the%20only%20surviving%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20who%20was%20not%20put%20under%20preventive%20detention%20when%20Article%20370%20was%20read%20down%20by%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20three%20%E2%80%93%20Farooq%20Abdullah%2C%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%20and%20Omar%20Abdullah%20%E2%80%93%20were%20detained%20under%20the%20draconian%20Public%20Safety%20Act%20for%20months.%20Azad%20alleged%20that%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Crumours%E2%80%9D%20in%202019%20that%20the%20NC%20leaders%20urged%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20to%20keep%20them%20under%20detention%20after%20Article%20370%20was%20read%20down%20to%20avoid%20public%20wrath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELashing%20out%20at%20the%20former%20Congress%20leader%2C%20Omar%20claimed%20that%20Azad%20had%20%E2%80%9Cbegged%E2%80%9D%20his%20party%20for%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20seat%20in%202015.%20He%20also%20alleged%20that%20Azad%20was%20hobnobbing%20with%20the%20BJP%20to%20damage%20the%20NC%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20prospects%20in%20the%20Chenab%20Valley%2C%20his%20home%20turf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20by%20Azad%20also%20angered%20the%20NC%20camp%2C%20with%20all%20top%20leaders%20and%20the%20NC%E2%80%99s%20media%20cell%20supervisors%2C%20including%20the%20chief%20spokesperson%20Tanvir%20Sadiq%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20additional%20spokesperson%20Sarah%20Hayat%20Shah%2C%20besides%20other%20lower%20rung%20activists%2C%20taking%20to%20social%20media%20to%20denounce%20Azad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20a%20minor%20observation.%20I%20can%20comprehend%20novices%20and%20the%20ungrateful%20speaking%20out%20(though%20he%20falls%20into%20that%20category%20too-%20Twice%20helped%20by%20NC%20to%20become%20Raj%20Sabha%20MP)%2C%20but%20I%20fail%20to%20grasp%20how%20a%20Union%20minister%20and%20former%20CM%20has%20stooped%20to%20such%20depths.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20shameless%3B%20it%20surpasses%20that.%20I%20wish%20he%20had%20refrained%20from%20engaging%20in%20corruption%20altogether%2C%20no%20one%20would%20have%20ever%20threatened%20him%20with%20jail%20or%20eviction%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sadiq%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Peoples%20Democratic%20Party%20also%20joined%20the%20political%20slugfest%20with%20Iltija%20Mufti%2C%20daughter%20and%20media%20advisor%20of%20the%20party%20president%20Mehbooba%20Mufti%2C%20posting%20a%20tweet%20by%20India%20Today%20which%20showed%20a%20picture%20of%20Azad%20and%20his%20purported%20quote%3A%20%E2%80%98Abdullahs%20secretly%20meet%20PM%20Modi%20at%20night%3A%20Ghulam%20Nabi%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNight%20Rendezvous%E2%80%9D%20Iltija%20posted%20on%20X%20with%20an%20owl%20emoji%20and%20a%20yellow%20face%20with%20a%20hand%20on%20mouth%2C%20indicating%20shock%20or%20surprise.%20The%20tweet%2C%20which%20had%2042k%20impressions%20with%20over%20100%20retweets%20and%20likes%20at%20the%20time%20when%20this%20story%20was%20drafted%2C%20agitated%20the%20NC%E2%80%99s%20social%20media%20activists%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20NC%20activist%20replied%20to%20Iltija%20with%20a%20photo%20which%20showed%20her%20standing%20between%20Mehbooba%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20at%20the%20wedding%20reception%20of%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20Jay%20Shah%2C%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20on%20February%2016%2C%202015%2C%20a%20month%20before%20the%20PDP%20formed%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20activist%20replied%20with%20a%20photo%20showing%20Mehbooba%20and%20BJP%20leader%20Murli%20Manohar%20Joshi%20sharing%20a%20light%20moment%20while%20L.K.%20Advani%20and%20Amit%20Shah%20are%20in%20the%20background.%20The%20photo%20was%20taken%20on%20March%201%2C%202015%20when%20the%20PDP-BJP%20coalition%20government%20was%20sworn%20in%20with%20late%20Mufti%20Sayeed%20as%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAzad%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20came%20barely%20days%20after%20a%20BJP%20leader%20from%20Jammu%2C%20Devendra%20Rana%2C%20claimed%20that%20NC%20leaders%20had%20offered%20to%20form%20a%20coalition%20government%20with%20the%20BJP%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20after%20the%202014%20assembly%20election%20and%20again%20in%202018%20when%20Mufti%20passed%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%20claimed%20that%20the%20saffron%20party%