3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20(February%2019)%20said%20that%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20faction%20can%20use%20%E2%80%98Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20%E2%80%93%20Sharad%20Chandra%20Pawar%E2%80%99%20as%20its%20name%20till%20further%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-sharad-pawar-faction-nationalist-congress-party-sharad-chandra-pawar-249892%3Finfinitescroll%3D1%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20made%20these%20remarks%20while%20hearing%20a%20plea%20filed%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%20challenging%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20recognise%20Ajit%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20faction%20as%20the%20authentic%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20also%20allowed%20him%20to%20approach%20the%20Commission%20for%20allocation%20of%20a%20party%20symbol%2C%20directing%20the%20poll%20panel%20to%20allot%20it%20within%20one%20week%20of%20the%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20court%20session%20last%20Friday%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20brought%20up%20this%20petition%20before%20Chief%20Justice%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20pressing%20for%20an%20urgent%20listing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinghvi%20highlighted%20the%20imminent%20risk%20of%20Sharad%20Pawar%20facing%20disciplinary%20action%20from%20Ajit%20Pawar%20during%20the%20upcoming%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20Session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20the%20urgency%2C%20Singhvi%20pointed%20out%20that%20Sharad%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20faction%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20allocated%20any%20party%20symbol%2C%20leaving%20them%20susceptible%20to%20Ajit%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20directives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Monday%E2%80%99s%20hearing%2C%20Singhvi%20appealed%20to%20the%20court%20to%20extend%20the%20interim%20arrangement%2C%20as%20approved%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20which%20allows%20the%20use%20of%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Nationalist%20Congress%20Party-Sharad%20Chandra%20Pawar%E2%80%99%20until%20the%20conclusion%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20elections%20on%20February%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20he%20requested%20the%20court%20to%20instruct%20the%20commission%20to%20issue%20a%20symbol%20promptly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20counsel%20also%20cited%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20interim%20order%20in%20a%20similar%20petition%20filed%20by%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%2C%20contesting%20the%20Election%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20recognise%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20as%20the%20official%20Shiv%20Sena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20court%20declined%20to%20halt%20the%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20order%20last%20year%2C%20it%20allowed%20the%20Uddhav%20group%20to%20maintain%20the%20name%20%E2%80%98Shiv%20Sena%20(Uddhav%20Balasaheb%20Thackeray)%E2%80%99.%20The%20court%20also%20permitted%20the%20flaming%20torch%20symbol%20during%20the%20pendency%20of%20the%20matter.%20This%20was%20also%20granted%20by%20the%20commission%20for%20the%20Maharashtra%20assembly%20bye-elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708416034000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F10162747%2FUntitled-design-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-allows-use-of-nationalist-congress-party-sharad-chandra-pawar-name-until-further-orders%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20apex%20court%20made%20these%20remarks%20while%20hearing%20a%20plea%20filed%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%20challenging%20the%20Election%20Commission's%20decision%20to%20recognise%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20faction%20as%20the%20authentic%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-allows-use-of-nationalist-congress-party-sharad-chandra-pawar-name-until-further-orders%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D