0Tips%20From%20Homemaker%20Who%20Earns%20Rs%201%20Lakh%2FMonth%20Selling%20Them%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20finishing%20her%20household%20chores%2C%20what%20Viji%20Abi%20eagerly%20anticipates%20in%20her%20daily%20routine%20is%20caring%20for%20her%20home%20garden%20and%20engaging%20with%20her%20gardening%20friends%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20entering%20her%20garden%20in%20Thrissur%2C%20Kerala%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20be%20welcomed%20by%20a%20vibrant%20display%20of%20blooming%20flowers.%20However%2C%20the%20standout%20feature%20of%20the%20garden%20is%20her%20water%20lily%20pots%20containing%20exotic-coloured%20lilies.%20As%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20few%20water%20lily%20hybridisers%2C%20Viji%E2%80%99s%20garden%20proudly%20showcases%20a%20hybrid%20variety%20she%20cultivated%20called%20Nymphaea%20Sree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGardening%20started%20as%20a%20leisure%20activity%20but%20transformed%20into%20my%20passion.%20I%20was%20inquisitive%20about%20how%20lily%20plants%20are%20grown%20and%20which%20variety%20survives.%20Now%2C%20I%20earn%20more%20than%20Rs%201%20lakh%20a%20month%20by%20selling%20lilies%20during%20a%20good%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViji%20shares%20the%20secrets%20behind%20her%20healthy%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F208990%2Fsustainable-garden-green-peace-home-garden-indoor-plants-garden-workshops-char01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreen%20garden%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20how%20you%20too%20can%20grow%20water%20lilies%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EJourney%20to%20her%20magic%20garden%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20with%20an%20affinity%20for%20plants%20and%20greenery%2C%20Viji%20has%20been%20fond%20of%20gardening%20for%20most%20of%20her%20life.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20must%20have%20been%20decades%20since%20I%20have%20been%20tending%20to%20a%20garden.%20It%20is%20my%20favourite%20th