This%20led%20to%20the%20foundation%20of%20Ambitio%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20AI%20admissions%20platform%2C%20to%20help%20applicants%20secure%20admissions%20to%20top%20global%20universities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirghayu%20explains%20in%20detail%20how%20Ambitio%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340888%2Fshark-tank-cybersecurity-app-artificial-intelligence-ai-pratyusha-vemuri-online-fraud-transactions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euses%20AI%20to%20help%20students%20%3C%2Fa%3Esecure%20admissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENot%20his%20first%20try%20at%20entrepreneurship%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20graduation%20from%20IIT-BHU%2C%20Dirghayu%20Kaushik%20got%20a%20job%20in%20a%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20got%20hired%20as%20a%20founding%20member%20in%20a%20startup.%20For%20about%20two%20years%2C%20I%20spearheaded%20their%20entire%20product%20development%2C%20overseeing%20the%20creation%20of%20both%20the%20tech%20and%20product%20teams%20from%20scratch.%20We%20started%20with%20just%20a%20four-member%20team%2C%20including%20the%20founders%2C%20and%20expanded%20significantly%20during%20my%20tenure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20was%20working%20at%20the%20startup%2C%20he%20was%20also%20looking%20for%20colleges%20to%20further%20his%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20completed%20my%20graduation%20and%20started%20to%20look%20for%20foreign%20universities%20to%20apply%20for%20an%20MBA.%20The%20process%20was%20tedious%20and%20I%20realised%20that%20there%20was%20no%20platform%20to%20help%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20counsellors%20who%20help%20students%20get%20into%20universities%20but%20they%20charge%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20which%20might%20not%20be%20affordable%20to%20everyone.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20can%20help%20you%20with%20particular%20college%20admission%20and%20not%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20colleges%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirghayu%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20platform%20that%20did%20it%20all%20for%20students%20%E2%80%94%20college%20applications%2C%20personal%20essays%2C%20and%20finding%20the%20right%20college%20for%20the%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20my%20college%20buddies%20%E2%80%94%20Vikrant%20Shivalik%20and%20Vaibhav%20Tyagi%20%E2%80%94%20and%20told%20them%20about%20my%20idea.%20They%20were%20enthralled%20and%20we%20joined%20hands%20to%20create%20the%20platform%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-12-1708005010.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20founders%20of%20Ambitio.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-12-1708005010.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-12-1708005010-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-12-1708005010-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-12-1708005010-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-12-1708005010-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341975%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20founders%20of%20Ambitio.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trio%20developed%20the%20platform%20and%20launched%20it%20in%202023.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20began%20by%20assembling%20a%20cohort%20of%2025%20students%20and%20then%20assisted%20them%20in%20securing%20placements%20at%20top%20institutions.%20Prior%20to%20developing%20any%20product%2C%20we%20focused%20on%20refining%20their%20profiles.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20initiated%20this%20process%20by%20leveraging%20notion%20templates%2C%20air%20tables%2C%20and%20other%20local%20tools%20to%20create%20a%20small%20MVP%20(Minimum%20Viable%20Product).%20Through%20these%20means%2C%20we%20meticulously%20analysed%20how%20we%20could%20enhance%20their%20chances%20of%20gaining%20admission%20to%20reputable%20institutions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%20further.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20various%20students%20who%20have%20availed%20of%20their%20services%20is%20Prakhar%20Kamal%20who%20got%20into%20Warwick%20Business%20School.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20already%20working%20with%20a%20counsellor%20before%20I%20knew%20about%20Ambitio.%20My%20experience%20with%20the%20counsellor%20was%20not%20very%20good%20and%20I%20lost%20motivation.%20When%20I%20started%20to%20use%20Ambitio%2C%20I%20started%20to%20regain%20confidence%20in%20myself.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20use%20their%20services%20to%20find%20the%20colleges%20that%20suit%20me%20and%20then%20choose%20the%20right%20one%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20its%20operation%2C%20the%20platform%20has%20helped%20over%20175%20students%20get%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F65140%2Fiit-bombays-matsya-international-robot-submarine-building-competition%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternational%20universities%3C%2Fa%3E%20such%20as%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20University%2C%20NYU%2C%20Imperial%20College%20Dundon%2C%20UC%20Berkeley%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUsing%20AI%20to%20find%20the%20dream%20college%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-11-1708004888.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20company%20has%20helped%20175%20students%20get%20their%20dream%20university.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-11-1708004888.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-11-1708004888-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-11-1708004888-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-11-1708004888-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-11-1708004888-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341973%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20company%20has%20helped%20175%20students%20get%20their%20dream%20university.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbitio%20began%20with%20a%20core%20challenge%20we%20aimed%20to%20address%3A%20simplifying%20the%20admissions%20process%20for%20students%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20achieve%20this%2C%20we%20developed%20a%20platform%20product%20designed%20to%20support%20students%20throughout%20their%20entire%20admissions%20journey.%20Our%20ultimate%20objective%20is%20to%20establish%20a%20comprehensive%20global%20AI%20admissions%20platform%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CRegardless%20of%20a%20student%E2%80%99s%20background%20or%20location%2C%20our%20aim%20is%20to%20provide%20equal%20opportunities%20and%20access%20to%20the%20right%20guidance%2C%20a%20privilege%20often%20reserved%20for%20the%20affluent%20or%20those%20able%20to%20afford%20expensive%20counsellors.%20We%20leverage%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F126973%2Fkerala-police-equips-personnel-cutting-edge-body-cameras%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecutting-edge%20technology%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20including%20AI%2C%20to%20achieve%20this%20goal.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20AI%20comes%20into%20play%20with%20the%20process%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20employ%20AI%20in%20two%20primary%20areas.%20Firstly%2C%20we%20utilise%20it%20to%20assist%20students%20in%20determining%20the%20most%20suitable%20program%20or%20university%20currently%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20While%20there%20are%20existing%20filtration%20tools%20enabling%20students%20to%20filter%20courses%20they%20are%20eligible%20for%20and%20view%20them%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20taken%20an%20additional%20step%20forward.%20We%20incorporate%20preferences%20into%20the%20equation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20the%20AI%20strives%20to%20understand%20and%20integrate%20the%20individual%20preferences%20of%20each%20student%20into%20the%20recommendations%20that%20it%20provides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20accomplish%20this%20through%20our%20proprietary%20recommendation%20engine%2C%20which%20has%20been%20trained%20on%20over%2015%20million%20acceptance%20and%20admit%20data%20points.%20While%20it%E2%80%99s%20certainly%20possible%20for%20students%20to%20conduct%20this%20research%20themselves%20by%20visiting%20numerous%20websites%2C%20reading%20various%20articles%2C%20and%20compiling%20the%20information%20manually%2C%20our%20platform%20streamlines%20this%20process%20significantly%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20synthesising%20and%20analysing%20vast%20amounts%20of%20information%2C%20the%20platform%20can%20deliver%20personalised%20recommendations%20quickly%20and%20seamlessly%2C%20saving%20students%20valuable%20time%20and%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20step%20where%20AI%20comes%20in%20to%20help%20the%20students%20is%20writing%20their%20personal%20essays.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20students%20know%20what%20college%20they%20want%2C%20the%20next%20step%20is%20to%20write%20a%20stellar%20essay.%20We%20trained%20our%20model%20with%205%2C000%20accepted%20essays%20from%20across%20universities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20begin%20by%20ensuring%20basic%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F341068%2Fteach-spoken-english-on-youtube-dehati-madam-uttar-pradesh-yashoda-lodhi-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrammar%20and%20punctuation%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20correct.%20Beyond%20these%20fundamentals%2C%20we%20focus%20on%20delivery%20and%20specificity.%20Delivery%20pertains%20to%20how%20effectively%20the%20essay%20is%20conveyed%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20while%20specificity%20refers%20to%20its%20relevance%20to%20the%20programme%20being%20applied%20for%20and%20the%20individual%20applicant%E2%80%99s%20profile.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqYHd6FBTi0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqYHd6FBTi0%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCqYHd6FBTi0%2F%3Futm_source%