a%20100%20percent%20green%20hydrogen%20plant%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%20would%20be%20the%20first%20operative%20green%20hydrogen%20production%20facility%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20will%20produce%20energy%20without%20emitting%20carbon%20dioxide%20into%20the%20atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Amit%20Bansal%2C%20CEO%20of%20Hygenco%20Green%20Energies%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20rapid%20pace%20of%20growth%20is%20already%20entailing%20a%20significant%20surge%20in%20the%20use%20of%20resources%2C%20especially%20fossil%20fuels.%20With%20over%2080%20percent%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F142537%2Findian-origin-scientist-team-fuel-from-sunlight%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20India%E2%80%99s%20fuel%20requirements%20%3C%2Fa%3Ebeing%20import-dependent%20and%20coal%20being%20the%20primary%20source%20of%20its%20electricity%20generation%2C%20there%20is%20a%20significant%20need%20to%20tap%20all%20forms%20of%20alternative%20energy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fhygenco-1707917590.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22While%20working%20in%20the%20renewable%20energy%20sector%2C%20Amit%20wanted%20to%20work%20towards%20addressing%20India%E2%80%99s%20energy%20crises.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fhygenco-1707917590.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fhygenco-1707917590-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fhygenco-1707917590-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fh