0hydrogen%20include%2C%20energy%20independence%2C%20achieving%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20net%20zero%20targets%2C%20and%20creating%20huge%20job%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20save%20our%20forex.%20The%20precious%20foreign%20exchange%20saved%20by%20reducing%20fossil%20fuel%20imports%20can%20be%20harnessed%20for%20social%20use%20such%20as%20health%20and%20education.%20Further%2C%20the%20country%20can%20even%20target%20to%20become%20a%20net%20exporter%20of%20ammonia%20and%20its%20derivatives%20from%20being%20a%20large%20importer%20of%20fossil%20fuels%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20Amit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CGreen%20hydrogen%20and%20its%20derivatives%20as%20fuel%20can%20decarbonise%20hard-to-abate%20sectors%2C%20especially%20since%20these%20sectors%20contribute%20nearly%2080%20percent%20of%20carbon%20footprint.%20This%20will%20be%20crucial%20as%20conventional%20electricity%20replacement%20by%20100%20percent%20green%20electricity%20will%20only%20result%20in%2020%20percent%20decarbonisation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20the%20most%20of%20a%20growing%20demand%20for%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20Amit%20launched%20Hygenco%20in%202020%20with%20a%20vision%20to%20help%20India%20achieve%20energy%20independence%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20climate%20challenges%20continue%20to%20rise%2C%20and%20ensure%20a%20sustainable%20future%20for%20the%20coming%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-4-1707917279.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hygenco%20Green%20Energies%20signed%20a%20green%20hydrogen%20and%20green%20oxygen%20long-term%20offtake%20agreement%20with%20Sterlite%20Technologies%20Limited.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.co