my%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20body-positive%20content%20creator%20in%20this%20space%2C%20Diksha%20has%20created%20content%20ranging%20from%20recommendations%20of%20brands%20that%20make%20apparel%20in%20plus%20sizes%20to%20%5Bverbal%5D%20comebacks%20against%20relatives%20saying%20things%20about%20her%20physical%20appearance.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20shared%20such%20content%20all%20across%20my%20personal%20social%20media%20page.%20Through%20making%20such%20content%2C%20I%20became%20that%20elder%20sister%20or%20friend%20%5Bto%20my%20followers%5D%20that%20I%20never%20had%20when%20I%20was%20a%20child%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20content%20creator%20to%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGrowing%20up%20in%20a%20%E2%80%98business%20family%E2%80%99%2C%20Diksha%20always%20had%20the%20desire%20to%20start%20one%20herself.%20But%20the%20decision%20to%20establish%20%E2%80%98A%20Little%20Extra%E2%80%99%20in%20August%202020%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20following%20a%20family%20tradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20I%20was%20experimenting%20with%20fashion%20but%20there%20weren%E2%80%99t%20enough%20clothes%20%5Bthat%20fit%20my%20size%5D%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20So%2C%20I%20started%20employing%20different%20accessories%20to%20look%20more%20fashionable.%20Even%20while%20travelling%20to%20different%20countries%2C%20particularly%20in%20Asia%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20clothes%20for%20people%20my%20size.%20My%20idea%20was%20to%20always%20shop%20for%20jewellery%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20my%20friends%20went%20to%20the%20mall%20and%20shopped%20for%20clothes%2C%20I%20also%20wanted%20something%20to%20shop%20for.%20So%2C%20I%20would%20visit%20the%20jewellery%20section%20because%20the%20items%20on%20sale%20there%20did%20not%20come%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20size%20limitations%20you%20see%20in%20apparel%20