re%2C%20the%20second%20step%20is%20clinical%20evaluation%20and%20diagnosis.%20Facilities%20like%20the%20DEIC%20should%20be%20able%20to%20help%20in%20this%20step.%20The%20last%20and%20most%20crucial%20step%20is%20accessibility%20to%20treatment.%20As%20the%20majority%20of%20public%20hospitals%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303740%2Fresearcher-quits-job-to-build-non-invasve-device-to-detect-breast-cancer-thermalytix-niramai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaediatric%20oncology%20care%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20parents%20either%20have%20to%20take%20them%20far%20to%20a%20government%20hospital%20that%20has%20the%20treatment%2C%20or%20go%20to%20a%20private%20hospital%20nearby.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20role%20of%20trusts%20like%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20is%20very%20important%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20as%20they%20help%20families%20afford%20quality%20healthcare%20and%20save%20the%20lives%20of%20their%20children%20through%20timely%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kalra%20says%20that%20his%20biggest%20request%20to%20parents%20is%20to%20continue%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CParents%20must%20remain%20hopeful%20and%20continue%20treatment.%20The%20results%20are%20good%20and%20most%20children%20do%20well%2C%20after%20early%20diagnosis.%20We%20are%20thankful%20to%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%20which%20makes%20it%20possible%20for%20so%20many%20children%20to%20access%20treatment%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Kalra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hans%20Bal%20Arogya%20Karyakram%2C%20which%20has%20been%20working%20on%20ground%20since%202017%2C%20has%20helped%20over%202%2C518%20children.%20A%20medical%20audit%20found%20that%20the%20survival%20rates%20of%20children%20had%20improved%20by%20more%20than%2080%25%20post-intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20success%20of%20and%20the%20learnings%20from%20the%20programme%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20The%20Hans%20Foundatio