20are%20present%20at%20birth%20and%20can%20affect%20the%20structure%20of%20a%20baby%E2%80%99s%20heart%20and%20the%20way%20it%20works.%20They%20can%20affect%20how%20blood%20flows%20through%20the%20heart%20and%20out%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20body.%20CHDs%20can%20vary%20from%20mild%20(such%20as%20a%20small%20hole%20in%20the%20heart)%20to%20severe%20(such%20as%20missing%20or%20poorly%20formed%20parts%20of%20the%20heart).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F30745481%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Library%20of%20Medicine%3C%2Fa%3E%20stated%20that%20nine%20out%20of%201%2C000%20babies%20have%20CHD.%20In%20India%2C%20more%20than%20two%20lakh%20babies%20are%20estimated%20to%20have%20this%20condition%20annually.%20One-fifth%20of%20these%20babies%20will%20likely%20need%20intervention%20in%20the%20first%20year%20of%20their%20life%2C%20due%20to%20a%20serious%20birth%20defect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%2C%20though%2C%20is%20twofold%2C%20as%20early%20and%20timely%20intervention%20is%20of%20prime%20importance%20in%20this%20disease.%20But%20specialised%20care%20is%20lacking%20in%20most%20government%20institutions%2C%20which%20causes%20a%20financial%20constraint%20on%20parents%20with%20low%20incomes%2C%20like%20Wahida.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWahida%20found%20help%20through%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%2C%20a%20charitable%20trust%2C%20which%2C%20through%20its%20%E2%80%98Little%20Hearts%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20has%20helped%20over%203%2C000%20children%20with%20CHD%20in%20the%20past%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20timely%20intervention%20is%20key%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FScreenshot-578-1-min-1